(20, 1, 'Abpress Eye Drop', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nAbpress Eye Drop is a prescription that is used for the treatment of pressure in the eyes (ocular hypertension) and glaucoma. It works by decreasing the pressure of fluid in the eye (aqueous humor), which helps in lowering the increased eye pressure.\r\nAbpress Eye Drop is to be used only in the affected eye. \r\nUSES OF ABPRESS EYE DROP\r\nIn Ocular hypertension\r\nOcular hypertension is a condition where the pressure inside the eye is higher than normal eye pressure due to fluid build-up. Abpress Eye Drop increases the flow of fluid from inside the eye into the bloodstream thereby lowering the increased eye pressure. This prevents further damage or complications such as change in vision or even loss of vision. You should only use Abpress Eye Drop in the affected eye and take it regularly as prescribed by your doctor.\r\nIn Glaucoma\r\nGlaucoma is an eye disease that damages the optic nerve which is essential for proper vision. This damage is often caused by an abnormally high pressure in the eye. Abpress Eye Drop is used to reduce swelling and pressure inside the eye. This helps prevent complications of glaucoma such as blindness and improves the vision. This medicine may be used alone or with other eye drops. Glaucoma cannot be prevented. Frequent monitoring, regular checkups can help detect the disease in its early stages.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607593624.jpeg', '', 235.70, NULL, '5 ml in 1 packet', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 09:06:19', '2020-12-10 15:17:04'),
(21, 1, 'Absolut 3G Capsule', 'Information \r\nAbsolut 3G capsules helps to treat fatigue, stress, weakness & exhaustion, improves physical performance, retard degenerative processes of agening and improve body resistance top infections. Absolut 3G capsules also fight free radicals damaging effects and exhibit positive effect on growth, energy and appetite.\r\n\r\nKey Ingredients:\r\nOmega-3 Fatty acid\r\nGreen tea extract\r\nGinkgo biloba\r\nGinseng\r\nGrape seed extract\r\nAntioxidants\r\nVitamins\r\nMinerals\r\nTrace elements\r\n\r\nKey Benefits:\r\nGinseng in absolute 3G capsule is an adaptogen, a helps reduce fatigue stress in the body\r\nEffective in cancer, lowering LDL cholesterol levels, & inhibit the abnormal formation of blood clots\r\nTreats depression, memory loss in the elderly, and sexual problems\r\nAbsolute 3g capsules acts as anti-bacterial, anti-viral & anti-inflammatory\r\nInhibit cholesterol biosynthesis & decreases reactive oxygen species (ROS)\r\nThe vitamins, minerals & antioxidant in absolute 3G capsule enhances different immune functions\r\n \r\nDirection For Use\r\nOne capsule to taken once daily after meal with water or as directed by the physician.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/150321_09_46_13.jpg', '', 196.00, NULL, '10 Capsules in 1 Strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 09:13:46', '2020-12-10 15:42:11'),
(22, 1, 'Absolut DM Capsule', 'Information \r\nAbsolut DM is fortified with Alpha lipoic acid, Benfotiamine, Folic acid, Mecobalamin and Pyridoxine. Absolut DM works as a supplement in diabetic patients. It reduces the risk of various Diabetic complications such as CVDs, Diabetic retinopathy, Diabetic nephropathy and Diabetic nephropathy.\r\n \r\nBenfotiamine reduces the production of advanced glycation end products (AGE), which may lead to diabetic complications. It also corrects glucose-induced endothelial cell damage and corrects thiamine deficiency. Benfothiamine majorly decreases  the incidence of neuropathies.\r\nBenfothiamine also lowers HbA1c in diabetic neuropathy.\r\n \r\nBiotin improves glucose metabolism & enhances muscle insulin sensitivity. Pyridoxine, Mecobalamin and folic acid in Absolut DM enhances nervous conduction and also helps in bringing down the plasma level of homocysteine, the major risk factor for Diabetic complications. Alpha lipoic acid is a universal antioxidant that reduces the Free radicals further lowering down the risk of diabetic complications.\r\n \r\nUse under medical supervision', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607422106.jpeg', '', 170.00, NULL, '10 Capsules in 1 Strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 09:14:46', '2020-12-08 15:38:26'),
(23, 15, 'Abzorb Anti Fungal Powder', 'Information\r\nAbzorb Anti-Fungal Powder is a topical antifungal dusting powder. It is recommended wherever excess moisture aggravates heat or friction rashes. The abzorb antifungal is prescribed for local fungal infections.\r\n\r\nKey Ingredients:\r\nClotrimazole\r\n\r\nKey Benefits:\r\nPrevents fungal growth on the skin and controls itching\r\nUseful wherever excess perspiration or exudates need absorption\r\nSoothes irritated skin and protects against chafing and rash\r\nHelps fight fungal infections, prevent recurrence and provide soothing maintenance therapy\r\nDirections For Use:\r\nUse as directed by the physician.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607422185.jpeg', '', 126.00, NULL, '100GM', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 08:29:22', '2020-12-08 15:39:45'),
(24, 1, 'Acamprol Tablet', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nAcamprol Tablet is a medicine that is used to stop craving in people who have completely stopped drinking alcohol. However, this medicine does not treat alcohol withdrawal symptoms or prevent the harmful effects of alcohol abuse.\r\nUSES OF ACAMPROL TABLET\r\nIn Alcohol addiction\r\nAcamprol Tablet is a medicine used, along with social support and counseling, to help people recover from alcohol addiction and to avoid having the urge to drink alcohol again. Acamprol Tablet starts working from the very first dose and is a very safe and effective way of treating alcohol addiction.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607422356.jpeg', '', 82.00, NULL, '6 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 13:33:50', '2020-12-08 15:42:36'),
