(63, 1, 'Acivir Cream', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nAcivir Cream is an antiviral medicine which helps in treating skin infections caused by Herpes simplex virus such as herpes labialis. It prevents the multiplication of the virus in skin cells and therefore helps in clearing the skin infection. \r\nAcivir Cream is for external use only. \r\nUSES OF ACIVIR CREAM\r\nIn Herpes labialis\r\nHerpes labialis, commonly known as cold sores, is a viral infection that primarily affects the lip. Symptoms typically include a burning pain followed by small blisters or sores. Acivir Cream can speed up healing of herpes labialis and also prevent recurrence of the sores. ', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/270221_12_29_03.jpg', '', 110.00, NULL, 'TUBE OF 10 GM', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 13:05:08', '2020-12-09 13:24:11'),
(64, 1, 'ACIVIR EYE OINTMENT', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nAcivir Eye Ointment is an antiviral medicine which treats eye infections caused by Herpes simplex virus. It works by preventing the multiplication of the virus on the surface of your eyeball (cornea). This stops the production of new viruses and clears up your eye infection. Acivir Eye Ointment is for external use only. \r\nUSES OF ACIVIR EYE OINTMENT\r\nIn Treatment of Eye infections by Herpes simplex virus\r\nAcivir Eye Ointment helps relieve symptoms of eye infections caused by Herpes simplex virus such as redness, swelling, itching and watering of eyes. This medicine kills the infection causing virus and prevents the further multiplication of the virus too. ', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/270221_12_54_05.jpg', '', 57.04, NULL, 'TUBE OF 5 GM', NULL, 0, '2021-02-27 12:06:19', '2020-12-09 13:25:28'),
