(67, 15, 'Acnestar 2.5% Soap', 'Information \r\nAcnestar soap is a deep cleansing bar contains benzoyl peroxide 2.5%.\r\nBenzoyl peroxide treats acne in three ways: by killing bacteria, peeling away dead skin cells and drying excess skin oil.\r\n \r\nBenzoyl peroxide is most effective in getting rid of the dirt accumulated to clear up the pores. Benzoyl peroxide works as a peeling agent. It increases skin turnover, clearing pores and reducing the bacterial count (specifically acnes) as well as acting directly as an antimicrobial.\r\n \r\nBenefits of Acnestar Soap:\r\nPenetrates pores quickly\r\nCleans and unclogs pores on the face, chest and back\r\nClears existing acne blemishes and helps prevent new blemishes from forming\r\nPromotes exfoliation of dead skin cells \r\n \r\nUse under medical supervision.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607501016.jpeg', '', 70.00, NULL, '1 box of 75 gm soap', NULL, 1, '2021-03-09 11:22:20', '2020-12-09 13:33:36'),
(68, 1, 'Acne-UV Gel SPF 30', 'Information \r\nAcne-UV Gel is a broad spectrum sunscreen that protects the skin against UVA and UVB rays by providing physical and chemical barrier to sunlight. Acne-UV Gel is a non-comedogenic which protects your skin from harmful rays.\r\nThis sunscreen lotion is suitable for normal skin and especially oily-acne prone skin.\r\n \r\nBenefits of Acne-UV Gel:\r\nBroad Spectrum: Physical & Chemical Protection against sun rays\r\nSPF 30: Blocks UVB rays\r\nUVA Protection: PA+++\r\nOil Free: Does not leave greasy feeling on the skin\r\nDermatologically Tested\r\n \r\nDirection for Use Acne-UV Gel:\r\nTake the sunscreen generously on your palm and apply on the exposed part of the skin\r\nApply atleast 20 minutes before getting under direct sunlight.\r\n \r\nUse under medical supervision.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/100321_08_15_55.jpg', '', 449.00, NULL, '1 tube of 30 gm gel', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:55:15', '2020-12-09 14:18:55'),
(70, 1, 'Acogut Tablet', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nAcogut Tablet is used in the treatment of indigestion. It also helps to relieve bloating after meals, pain in the upper abdomen and early satiety (feeling full after having a small amount of food).\r\nUSES OF ACOGUT TABLET\r\nIn Functional dyspepsia\r\nFunctional dyspepsia is another term for indigestion that is not associated with a specific cause. It may cause symptoms such as an early feeling of fullness after eating, stomach pain or discomfort, nausea, and bloating. Acogut Tablet helps treat these symptoms by increasing the rate of stomach emptying. Take it exactly as it is prescribed. Some simple lifestyle changes can help stop or reduce these symptoms. Think about what foods trigger your symptoms and try to avoid them; eat smaller, more frequent meals; try to lose weight if you are overweight and try to find ways to relax. Do not eat within 3 to 4 hours of going to bed.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607504976.jpeg', '', 197.95, NULL, 'STRIP OF 15 TABLETS', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:56:38', '2020-12-09 14:39:36'),
(71, 1, 'Acotrust Tablet', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nAcotrust Tablet is used in the treatment of indigestion. It also helps to relieve bloating after meals, pain in the upper abdomen and early satiety (feeling full after having a small amount of food).\r\nUSES OF ACOTRUST TABLET\r\nIn Functional dyspepsia\r\nFunctional dyspepsia is another term for indigestion that is not associated with a specific cause. It may cause symptoms such as an early feeling of fullness after eating, stomach pain or discomfort, nausea, and bloating. Acotrust Tablet helps treat these symptoms by increasing the rate of stomach emptying. Take it exactly as it is prescribed. Some simple lifestyle changes can help stop or reduce these symptoms. Think about what foods trigger your symptoms and try to avoid them; eat smaller, more frequent meals; try to lose weight if you are overweight and try to find ways to relax. Do not eat within 3 to 4 hours of going to bed.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607672972.jpeg', '', 198.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:52:13', '2020-12-11 13:19:32'),
(72, 15, 'Acscreen Sunscreen Gel SPF 47', 'Information \r\nAcscreen Sunscreen Gel SPF 47 is a non-comedogenic formula that is light on the skin and protects the skin from UVA I, UVA II and UVB. It has an oil-free formula which makes it ideal for oily, acne-prone skin.\r\n\r\nKey Ingredients:\r\nOctyl methoxy cinamate\r\nHomosalate\r\nOctrocrylene\r\nBenzophenone 3 (oxybenzone)\r\nAvobenzone\r\n\r\nKey Benefits:\r\nIt protects the skin from UVA I, UVA II and UVB rays\r\nIt prevents darkening of skin, sunburn and premature ageing\r\nIt has an oil-free formula which makes it ideal for oily, acne-prone skin\r\nIt is non-greasy, thus is light on the skin\r\nIt is a non-comedogenic, water-resistant sunscreen\r\n\r\nDirections For Use:\r\nUse as directed on the label.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607673370.png', '', 899.00, NULL, '50 ml gel in tube', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:50:06', '2020-12-11 13:26:10'),
(73, 1, 'ACTH INJECTION', 'INJECTION', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1610871088.jpg', '', 1964.46, NULL, '5 ml Injection in Vial', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:46:16', '2021-01-17 13:41:28'),
(74, 1, 'Actibile 300 Tablet', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nActibile 300 Tablet is a medicine used to dissolve certain types of gallstones, to prevent them from forming and to treat a type of liver disease called primary biliary cirrhosis. It is a bile acid which helps break down cholesterol which has formed into stones in your gallbladder.\r\nUSES OF ACTIBILE TABLET\r\nIn Primary biliary cirrhosis\r\nPrimary biliary cholangitis is a type of liver disease that gradually gets worse over time. It does not always have symptoms but, over time, it can lead to liver failure. Actibile 300 Tablet is used to treat this condition and may be used by itself or with other medicines. It can help prevent or delay liver damage in most people, especially if you start taking it in the early stages. Once you start this treatment, it is likely that you will be taking it for the rest of your life. To make the medicine more effective and for general health benefits, you can help yourself by stopping smoking, keeping a healthy weight, and not drinking too much alcohol.\r\nIn Gallbladder stones\r\nActibile 300 Tablet is a medicine that helps decreases the amount of cholesterol produced by your liver. It helps to break down cholesterol that has formed into “stones” in the gallbladder. It may take several months to completely dissolve the stone, so you need to take the medicine regularly and as long as the doctor has prescribed it for it to be effective.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607505603.jpeg', '', 285.10, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:43:18', '2020-12-09 14:50:03'),
(75, 1, 'Actibile 75 Tablet', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nActibile 75 Tablet is a medicine used to dissolve certain types of gallstones, to prevent them from forming and to treat a type of liver disease called primary biliary cirrhosis. It is a bile acid which helps break down cholesterol which has formed into stones in your gallbladder.\r\nUSES OF ACTIBILE TABLET\r\nIn Primary biliary cirrhosis\r\nPrimary biliary cholangitis is a type of liver disease that gradually gets worse over time. It does not always have symptoms but, over time, it can lead to liver failure. Actibile 75 Tablet is used to treat this condition and may be used by itself or with other medicines. It can help prevent or delay liver damage in most people, especially if you start taking it in the early stages. Once you start this treatment, it is likely that you will be taking it for the rest of your life. To make the medicine more effective and for general health benefits, you can help yourself by stopping smoking, keeping a healthy weight, and not drinking too much alcohol.\r\nIn Gallbladder stones\r\nActibile 75 Tablet is a medicine that helps decreases the amount of cholesterol produced by your liver. It helps to break down cholesterol that has formed into “stones” in the gallbladder. It may take several months to completely dissolve the stone, so you need to take the medicine regularly and as long as the doctor has prescribed it for it to be effective. There might be other medicines and certain lifestyle changes that can reduce your cholesterol level and make gallstones less likely, consult with your doctor.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607505779.jpeg', '', 106.30, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:41:02', '2020-12-09 14:52:59'),
(76, 1, 'Actigut Capsule', 'Information \r\nActigut capsules contains lactobacillus acidphilus which is beneficial in treating vaginal yeast infections, oral infections and urinary tract infections.\r\nApart from that these lactobacillus capsule also contains lactobacillus rhamosus, bifidobacterium longum, bifidobacterium bifidum among many others. Actigut capsules is to be used in cases of probiotic diarrhea treatment, vaginal yeast infections and other bacteria related infections in the mouth and intestines.\r\n\r\nBenefits of Actigut capsule:\r\nImproves bowel regularity and exhibits a preventive action against traveller\'s diarrhoea.\r\nFacilitates lactose digestion and turns out to be very effective in people with lactose intolerance.\r\nInhibits the growth of gram negative bacteria by producing lactic acid & digest the complex sugars.\r\nA Probiotic that helps to maintain and restore the natural flora in the large and small intestine.\r\n\r\n \r\nUse under medical supervision', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607505840.jpeg', '', 149.80, NULL, 'Strip of 10 Capsules', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:39:18', '2020-12-09 14:54:00'),
(78, 1, 'Actis C2 Tablet', 'Information\r\nActis C2 Tablet offers the oral form of bioactive collagen peptide in combination with glucosamine and hyaluronate. Glucosamine stimulates cartilage regeneration synergistically with collagen peptides.\r\n\r\nKey Ingredients:\r\nGlucosamine Hydrochloride\r\nCollagen Peptides\r\nSodium Hyaluronate\r\nVitamin C\r\nVitamin D3\r\n\r\nKey Benefits:\r\nHyaluronate improves synovial fluid consistency and volume, therefore, increasing cushioning action\r\nVitamin D3 and vitamin C help support cartilage regeneration\r\nACTIS C2 is an ideal supplement to help improve mobility in osteoarthritis\r\nIt helps to rebuild cartilage and improve joint stiffness\r\n\r\nDirections For Use:\r\nUse as directed by the physician.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/100321_08_21_38.jpg', '', 235.00, NULL, 'Strip of 10 tablets', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:38:21', '2020-12-11 13:28:32'),
(79, 1, 'Active D Capsule', 'Information \r\nActive D Capsule is used to treat problems related to Vitamin D deficiency. It is useful in osteoporosis, prevention of corticosteroid-induced osteoporosis among others.\r\n\r\nKey Ingredients:\r\nCalcitrol\r\n\r\nKey Benefits:\r\nCalcitriol regulates the bone and calcium homeostasis, which includes stimulating effects on osteoblastic activity in the skeleton\r\nHelps in the treatment of established osteoporosis with Calcitriol is associated with an increase in bone density and a reduction in new vertebral fractures\r\nIt is useful in osteoporosis, prevention of corticosteroid-induced osteoporosis, hypocalcaemia, hypoparathyroidism and hypophosphataemic rickets\r\n\r\nDirections For Use:\r\nAs prescribed by the Physician\r\nThe optimal daily dose of Active D Capsule must be carefully determined for each patient and indication\r\nDosage optimisation should be accompanied by regular monitoring of serum calcium concentration', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607506052.jpeg', '', 110.00, NULL, 'Strip of 10 Capsules', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:36:02', '2020-12-09 14:57:32'),
(80, 1, 'Actoid 25mg Capsule', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nActoid 25mg Capsule is a medicine that is similar to vitamin A and is involved in the normal growth of skin cells. It is used in the treatment of psoriasis. It works by stopping the overgrowth and thickening of skin cells.\r\nUSES OF ACTOID CAPSULE\r\nIn Psoriasis\r\nPsoriasis is a condition where the skin cells in the body grow too quickly and form scales and dry patches. They can grow anywhere, but most appear on the scalp, elbows, knees, and lower back. Actoid 25mg Capsule reduces the scaly, itchy patches along with other symptoms of inflammation such as redness, swelling or irritation which may develop on the different parts of the body. It also stops the overgrowth and thickening of the skin. Take it for as long as it is prescribed to get the most benefit. It may take several months to become fully effective. You should avoid drinking alcohol while having this treatment and drink plenty of water to stay hydrated.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/100321_08_47_34.jpg', '', 600.00, NULL, '10 capsules in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:34:47', '2020-12-09 15:15:34'),
(81, 5, 'ACTRAPID FLEXPEN 1*3ML', 'INSULIN', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607507258.jpeg', '', 471.80, NULL, '3ML', 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2020-12-09 15:17:38'),
