(98, 1, 'Adliv Forte Capsule', 'Information \r\nAdliv Forte Capsule tackles liver disorders of various forms and etiologies. Adliv Forte Capsule contains herbal extracts of Andrographis paniculata 250 mg, Picrorhiza kurroa 80 mg, Eclipta alba 250 mg, Phyllanthus niruri 250 mg. \r\n \r\nIt is used as a remedy in viral Hepatitis, drug induced or alcoholic hepatitis, hepatotoxicity due to anti-tubercular and anti-malarial drugs and all conditions of compromised liver and gall bladder functions. It is extremely useful in condition of decreased appetite due to liver disease. Adliv Forte Capsule also cures anorexia. \r\n \r\nIts herbal composition makes it absolutely free from side effects. \r\n \r\nUse under medical supervision', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607508423.jpeg', '', 53.50, NULL, '10 Capsules in 1 Strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 08:01:10', '2020-12-09 15:37:03'),
