(103, 1, 'ADMENTA 10 MG TABLET', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nADMENTA 10 MG TABLET is a medicine used in the treatment of Alzheimer\'s disease. It helps to slow down the progression of moderate to severe Alzheimer\'s by improving memory and thinking. This medicine works by blocking a chemical messenger involved in the transmission of nerve signals.\r\nUSES OF ADMENTA TABLET \r\nIn Alzheimer\'s disease\r\nADMENTA 10 MG TABLET MD improves learning, memory and information processing (cognitive function) in people with mild to moderate Alzheimer\'s disease. These problems in memory and thinking may start interfering with daily activities and worsen your condition. This medicine will help in managing Alzheimer’s disease effectively.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607509199.jpeg', '', 160.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 07:57:50', '2020-12-09 15:49:59'),
(104, 1, 'Admenta 5 Tablet', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nAdmenta 5 Tablet is a medicine used in the treatment of Alzheimer\'s disease. It helps to slow down the progression of moderate to severe Alzheimer\'s by improving memory and thinking. This medicine works by blocking a chemical messenger involved in the transmission of nerve signals.\r\nUSES OF ADMENTA TABLET\r\nIn Alzheimer\'s disease\r\nAdmenta 5 Tablet improves learning, memory and information processing (cognitive function) in people with mild to moderate Alzheimer\'s disease. These problems in memory and thinking may start interfering with daily activities and worsen your condition. This medicine will help in managing Alzheimer’s disease effectively.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/280221_09_16_47.jpg', '', 98.75, NULL, 'STRIP OF 10 TABLETS', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 13:00:53', '2020-12-09 15:53:14'),
(105, 1, 'Admoxy CV 625 Tablet', 'INTRODUCTION\r\nAdmoxy CV 625 Tablet is a penicillin-type of antibiotic that helps your body fight infections caused by bacteria. It is used to treat infections of the lungs (e.g., pneumonia), ear, nasal sinus, urinary tract, skin and soft tissue. It will not work for viral infections such as the common cold.\r\nUSES OF ADMOXY CV TABLET\r\nIn Bacterial infections\r\nAdmoxy CV 625 Tablet contains two different medicines, Amoxycillin and Clavulanic Acid, that work together to kill the bacteria that cause infections. Amoxycillin works by stopping the growth of bacteria. Clavulanic Acid reduces resistance and enhances the activity of Amoxycillin against bacteria.', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1607509470.jpeg', '', 180.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-10 07:55:46', '2020-12-09 15:54:30'),
