 level you will reduce the risk of getting any of the serious complications of diabetes such as kidney damage, eye damage, nerve problems, and loss of limbs. Taking this medicine regularly along with proper diet and exercise will help you live a normal, healthy life.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/280221_14_25_41.jpg', '', 139.18, NULL, 'STRIP OF 15 TABLETS', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 12:50:54', '2021-01-18 10:10:33');
