(393, 1, 'ANTIDEP 25MG TABLET', '<div><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Antidep 25mg Tablet is known as a tricyclic antidepressant. It is used to treat depression and bedwetting in children of age 6 years and above. It is also effective in treating depression that is unresponsive to other treatments.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ANTIDEP TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Bed-wetting</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Depression</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Antidep 25mg Tablet is thought to work by affecting the balance of certain chemicals (such as serotonin) in the brain. It helps improve mood and feelings of wellbeing, relieve anxiety and tension, help you sleep better, and increase your energy level. It is used to treat depression that is unresponsive to other medicines. You need to take it regularly as it is prescribed for it to be most effective and should not stop taking it suddenly.</span></div></div></div></div></div>', '', '', 10.00, NULL, 'STRIP OF 10 TABLETS', NULL, 0, '2021-02-18 10:39:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(394, 1, 'ANTIDEP 75MG TABLET', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Antidep 75 Tablet is known as a tricyclic antidepressant. It is used to treat depression and bedwetting in children of age 6 years and above. It is also effective in treating depression that is unresponsive to other treatments.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ANTIDEP TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Bed-wetting</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">In Depression</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Antidep 75 Tablet is thought to work by affecting the balance of certain chemicals (such as serotonin) in the brain. It helps improve mood and feelings of wellbeing, relieve anxiety and tension, help you sleep better, and increase your energy level. It is used to treat depression that is unresponsive to other medicines. You need to take it regularly as it is prescribed for it to be most effective and should not stop taking it suddenly.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611045061.jpg', '', 26.90, NULL, 'STRIP OF 10 TABLETS', NULL, 0, '2021-02-18 10:43:43', '2021-01-19 14:01:02'),
(396, 1, 'Anti-Thyrox 10 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Anti-Thyrox 10 Tablet belongs to a group of medicine called anti-thyroid agents. It is used in the treatment of hyperthyroidism. It reduces the amount of thyroid hormones produced by the thyroid gland.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ANTI-THYROX TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hyperthyroidism</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Anti-Thyrox 10 Tablet lessens the amount of thyroid hormone in your body and also helps relieve the symptoms of hyperthyroidism. These include palpitations, feeling anxious, sweaty or shaky and being intolerant to heat. This will help you have a better quality of life. Keep taking it as advised by the doctor to get maximum benefit.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1610972462.jpg', '', 388.10, NULL, 'Bottle of 100 tablets', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 09:13:06', '2021-01-18 17:51:02'),
(397, 1, 'Anti-Thyrox 5 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Anti-Thyrox 5 Tablet belongs to a group of medicine called anti-thyroid agents. It is used in the treatment of hyperthyroidism. It reduces the amount of thyroid hormones produced by the thyroid gland.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ANTI-THYROX TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hyperthyroidism</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Anti-Thyrox 5 Tablet lessens the amount of thyroid hormone in your body and also helps relieve the symptoms of hyperthyroidism. These include palpitations, feeling anxious, sweaty or shaky and being intolerant to heat. This will help you have a better quality of life. Keep taking it as advised by the doctor to get maximum benefit.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1610972640.jpg', '', 208.32, NULL, 'Bottle of 100 tablets', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 09:12:46', '2021-01-18 17:54:00'),
(398, 1, 'Antoxid Capsules', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Antoxid is an antioxidant capsule which contains Beta-carotene, Copper, manganese, Selenium, and Zinc sulphate.&nbsp;<br>Beta-carotene is a provitamin of vitamin A which is responsible for improving vision, proper functioning of the skin, development and functioning of the layer of skin known as epithelium. Beta-carotene is a very powerful antioxidant which kills the free radicals and reduce the oxidative stress, which may damage the structure of cell membrane and cause uncontrolled cell division. Beta-carotene accumulated in the skin protects it by absorbing sun radiation.&nbsp;<br>Multiminerals in Antioxid maintains a healthy functioning body, and contributes to healthy vibrant skin.<br>&nbsp;<br>Use under medical supervision</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611045274.jpg', '', 235.50, NULL, '30 Capsules in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 09:13:56', '2021-01-19 14:04:34'),
(399, 1, 'Antoxid -HC Capsule', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Antoxid -HC Capsule</span> is an antioxidant capsule is no. 1 dermatologist-recommended brand for skin protection. Beta-carotene is a provitamin of vitamin A which is responsible for improving vision, proper functioning of the skin, development and functioning of the layer of skin known as the epithelium. Beta-carotene is a very powerful antioxidant which kills the free radicals and reduces the oxidative stress, which may damage the structure of cell membrane and cause uncontrolled cell division.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Multi minerals in antioxid hc maintains a healthy functioning body and contribute to healthy vibrant skin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Beta-carotene in antoxid hc is accumulated in the skin which protects it by absorbing sun radiation.</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611045514.jpg', '', 442.75, NULL, '30 Capsules in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 09:14:22', '2021-01-19 14:08:34'),
(400, 1, 'Antoxid P Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Antoxid P Tablet</span> is used to help keep the body in a healthy state by treating various vitamin deficiencies like that of Vitamin A, D and E. It is also helpful in maintaining heart health and keeping heart related diseases at bay.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Beta Carotene in the tablet helps in protecting the skin from harmful sun radiation</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>The minerals in it helps in healthy functioning of the body</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It is helpful in treating Vitamin A, D and E deficiency</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It is used to help maintain heart health and thus prevent any heart associated diseases</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/180221_11_35_08.jpg', '', 308.00, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 09:14:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(401, 1, 'Antoxipan Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Antoxipan Tablet</span> is a nutritional supplement that contains essential minerals and vitamins that helps to provide nourishment to the body. It helps in growth, good health and has good antioxidant properties.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Methionine is useful in migraine, trigeminal neuralgia, cardiac arrhythmias</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Selenium has potent anti oxidant properties and helps to protect the cells</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Useful in vitamin C deficiencies</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Protects the body from harmful effects of oxidation</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Promotes growth and good health</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/180221_11_30_11.jpg', '', 350.00, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 09:14:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(402, 1, 'Anxipan Capsule', '<div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Anxipan Capsule is a combination of two medicines used to treat anxiety, acidity, and heartburn. It relaxes the nerves in the brain and also prevents excess acid formation in the stomach, indigestion, and heartburn that may be associated with anxiety.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">USES OF ANXIPAN CAPSULE</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Acidity</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Anxipan Capsule relieves excessive acidity in your stomach which prevents heartburn and indigestion. Usually, it is used along with other medicines for management of your condition.</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Heartburn</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Heartburn is a burning feeling in your chest caused by stomach acids travelling back up towards your throat and mouth (acid reflux). Anxipan Capsule improves the movement of food in the stomach and helps prevent heartburn.</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Anxiety</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Anxipan Capsule reduces the symptoms of excessive anxiety and worry. It can also reduce feelings of restlessness, tiredness, difficulty concentrating and feeling irritable. </span></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/050321_09_36_08.jpg', '', 107.00, NULL, '10 Capsules in 1 Strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 09:08:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
