of Edema</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\">Edema is caused by your body retaining too much water. Aquazide 25 Tablet helps get rid of the extra water and electrolytes from your body by increasing the amount of urine produced. This enables your body to get rid of extra water thereby relieving symptoms such as shortness of breath and swelling in your arms, legs or abdomen.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611048501.jpg', '', 18.80, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:53:45', '2021-01-19 14:58:21'),
(432, 1, 'Arachitol 3L Injection', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arachitol 3L Injection helps your body to absorb a mineral called calcium, which is important for maintaining strong bones. This medicine is used if your diet does not provide enough vitamin D and may be used to treat certain bone conditions such as thinning of the bones (osteoporosis).</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARACHITOL INJECTION</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Osteoporosis</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Osteoporosis is a common condition that weakens bones, making them fragile and more likely to break. It often occurs in women after menopause. Vitamin D is important for the absorption of calcium and helps regulate the amount of calcium and phosphate in your body. If you do not have enough calcium it can damage your bones. Normally your body creates vitamin D from sunlight, but you will be prescribed this medicine as a supplement if you do not have enough. It will help to keep your bones strong and healthy and reduce the risk of them becoming weak and more likely to break. It is important to keep taking it regularly to get the benefits.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Vitamin D deficiency</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Normally your body creates vitamin D from sunlight, but you will be prescribed this medicine as a supplement if you do not have enough. It is important to keep taking it regularly to get the benefits. You may not notice it working but keep taking it in order to protect your bones. Additionally, it can boost your immunity and increase the body\'s resistance against various infections.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611048661.jpg', '', 40.17, NULL, '1 ml Ampoule', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:52:41', '2021-01-19 15:01:01'),
(433, 1, 'Arachitol 6L Injection', '<h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 14px;\" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(33,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 33);=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" uppercase;=\"\" padding-top:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\"><b>INTRODUCTION</b></h2><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 14px;\" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(33,=\"\" 33,=\"\" 33);=\"\" text-transform:=\"\" uppercase;=\"\" padding-top:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\"><b><br></b></h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\">Arachitol 6L Injection helps your body to absorb a mineral called calcium, which is important for maintaining strong bones. This medicine is used if your diet does not provide enough vitamin D and may be used to treat certain bone conditions such as thinning of the bones (osteoporosis).</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\"><br></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARACHITOL INJECTION</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\"><br></span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Osteoporosis</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\">Osteoporosis is a common condition that weakens bones, making them fragile and more likely to break. It often occurs in women after menopause. Vitamin D is important for the absorption of calcium and helps regulate the amount of calcium and phosphate in your body. If you do not have enough calcium it can damage your bones. Normally your body creates vitamin D from sunlight, but you will be prescribed this medicine as a supplement if you do not have enough. It will help to keep your bones strong and healthy and reduce the risk of them becoming weak and more likely to break. It is important to keep taking it regularly to get the benefits.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\"><br></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Vitamin D deficiency</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" 8px=\"\" 0px=\"\" 16px;=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word;\"=\"\">Normally your body creates vitamin D from sunlight, but you will be prescribed this medicine as a supplement if you do not have enough. It is important to keep taking it regularly to get the benefits. You may not notice it working but keep taking it in order to protect your bones. Additionally, it can boost your immunity and increase the body\'s resistance against various infections.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611048739.jpg', '', 56.18, NULL, '1 ML AMPOULE', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:51:50', '2021-01-19 15:02:19'),
(434, 1, 'Arachitol Nano Oral Solution', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INFORMATION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Arachitol Nano Oral Solution</span> contains Cholecalciferol which is a form of fat-soluble Vitamin D. It is particularly beneficial in the treatment of bone disorders such as Osteomalacia, Osteoporosis, and Rickets. Arachitol Nano Syrup is used to treat calcium deficiency and helps to strengthen the bones. <br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamin D3 oral solution in Arachitol nano helps in the absorption of phosphorous and calcium from food and supplements</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It helps in the proper development and growth of the body</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It assists in the treatment of calcium deficiency</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>The formulation helps in the maintenance of strong bones and teeth</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/180221_13_40_26.jpg', '', 260.48, NULL, 'Packet of 4 bottle of 5 ml each', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:51:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(435, 1, 'Arachitol-O tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Arachitol-O tablet is fortified with Elemental Calcium and Vitamin D3<br>Calcium is used to prevent or treat low blood calcium levels in people who do not get enough calcium from their diets. Calcium is important for growth and development of bones. Arachitol-O tablet can help maintain calcium levels and help the body use calcium and phosphate to maintain healthy bones. Vitamin D3 is essential for the proper growth and development of the body. It is synthesized within the body after exposure to sunlight and is essential for many important functions of the human body. Vitamin D3 also helps the body to metabolize calcium and phosphate in the body.<br> <br>Arachitol-O tablet is used for treating conditions in which calcium metabolism is disturbed. It is also used in disorders associated with Vitamin D deficiency and in calcium malabsorption. <br>It helps in the development of bone mass, provide relief from muscle and bone pain, and also enhances metabolism. This is a dietary supplement that should be taken to avoid calcium disorders.  <br>Use under medical supervision.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/180221_13_27_29.jpg', '', 86.49, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:50:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(436, 1, 'Arbitel-AM Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arbitel-AM Tablet contains two medicines, both of which help to control high blood pressure. It lowers the blood pressure by relaxing the blood vessels and making it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. This will reduce your risk of having a heart attack or a stroke.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARBITEL-AM TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Both of the medicines in this combination work to lower blood pressure but in different ways. Together they help to relax blood vessels and make it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. This lowers blood pressure. If your blood pressure is controlled you are less at risk of having a heart attack, stroke, or kidney problems. The medicine must be taken regularly as prescribed to be effective.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611049065.jpg', '', 121.50, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:50:20', '2021-01-19 15:07:45'),
(437, 1, 'Arbitel 40 Tablet', '<p><b>                  INTRODUCTION\r\n</b></p><p>Arbitel 40 Tablet is a medicine used to treat high blood pressure and heart failure. Lowering blood pressure helps to prevent future heart attack and stroke. This medicine is also effective in preserving kidney function in patients with diabetes. Arbitel 40 Tablet can be prescribed either alone or in combination with other medicines. </p><p><b>\r\n\r\nUSES OF ARBITEL TABLET</b></p><p>\r\n\r\nIn Treatment of Hypertension (high blood pressure)</p><p><br></p><p>\r\nArbitel 40 Tablet relaxes the blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This effectively lowers the blood pressure. It must be taken regularly as prescribed to be effective.</p><p> \r\n\r\nIn Prevention of heart attack and stroke</p><p>\r\n</p><p>If your blood pressure is controlled you are less at risk of having a heart attack or stroke. Arbitel 40 Tablet reduces the chances of heart diseases and helps you remain healthier for longer. </p><p>\r\n\r\nIn Heart failure</p><p><br></p><p>\r\n</p><p>Heart failure means your heart is weak and cannot pump enough blood to your lungs and the rest of your body. The most common symptoms are breathlessness, tiredness, and swelling in your legs, ankles, abdomen, and other parts of your body. Arbitel 40 Tablet is an effective treatment for heart failure. This medicine will help relieve your symptoms, making you feel better and more energetic.\r\n              </p>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611049207.jpg', '', 72.24, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:49:27', '2021-01-19 15:10:07'),
(439, 1, 'Arbitel-CT 40 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arbitel-CT 40 Tablet contains two medicines, both of which help to control high blood pressure. Lowering blood pressure helps to reduce your risk of having a heart attack or a stroke in the future.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARBITEL-CT TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arbitel-CT 40 Tablet is a combination of two medicines namely Telmisartan and chlorthalidone. It is generally used when one medicine alone is not controlling your blood pressure effectively. Telmisartan works by relaxing and widening your blood vessels so your blood can flow more easily. This will lower your blood pressure. Chlorthalidone is known as a diuretic (water pill) which increases urine output thereby lowering blood pressure. If your blood pressure is controlled you are less at risk of having a heart attack, stroke, or kidney problems. The medicine must be taken regularly as prescribed to be effective. </div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611049601.jpg', '', 100.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:48:22', '2021-01-19 15:16:41'),
(440, 1, 'Arbitel-H Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arbitel-H Tablet contains two medicines, both of which help to control high blood pressure. It is generally used when one medicine alone is not controlling the blood pressure effectively. Lowering blood pressure helps to reduce your risk of having a heart attack or a stroke in the future.<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARBITEL-H TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arbitel-H Tablet is a combination of two medicines namely telmisartan and hydrochlorothiazide. It is generally used when one medicine alone is not controlling your blood pressure effectively. Telmisartan works by relaxing and widening your blood vessels so your blood can flow more easily. This will lower your blood pressure. Hydrochlorothiazide is known as a diuretic (water pill) which increases urine output thereby lowering blood pressure. If your blood pressure is controlled you are less at risk of having a heart attack, stroke, or kidney problems. The medicine must be taken regularly as prescribed to be effective. </div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611049749.jpg', '', 128.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:48:07', '2021-01-19 15:19:09'),
(441, 1, 'Arbivit 3 Forte Drop', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information about Arbivit -3 Forte Drop</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Arbivit 3 Forte Drop</span> is useful in bone related issues in kids. It is used to treat hypocalcaemia, hypoparathyroidism, hypophosphataemia, renal osteodystrophy and osteomalacia.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Used for treating bone related issues</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Used to treat hypocalcaemia, hypoparathyroidism, hypophosphataemia, renal osteodystrophy and osteomalacia</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Keeps bones healthy</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Useful for people who have kidney problems</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It works by helping the body to use more of the calcium found in foods and supplements</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br>Take as directed by the physician<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611049864.jpg', '', 68.20, NULL, 'Bottle of 15 ml', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:47:50', '2021-01-19 15:21:04'),
(442, 1, 'Arcalion Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arcalion Tablet is a prescription medicine indicated for the treatment of asthenia. Asthenia is a condition in which there is generalized tiredness and weakness that persists for a long term. It is used in combination with other medicines to improve everyday activities in Alzheimer\'s disease. Arcalion Tablet is also used to treat psychogenic erectile dysfunction. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARCALION TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Fatigue</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Fatigue or tiredness can make you dull and also affects the mood and thoughts. You are not able to perform at your full capacity both physically or mentally even in your daily life activities. This can affect your life adversely. Arcalion Tablet helps to treat this long term fatigue and makes you feel more energetic. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Alzheimer\'s disease</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arcalion Tablet improves learning, memory and information processing (cognitive function) in people with mild to moderate Alzheimer\'s disease. These problems in memory and thinking may start interfering with daily activities and worsen your condition. This medicine will help in managing Alzheimer’s disease effectively.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_10_38_16.jpg', '', 165.00, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:47:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(443, 1, 'A-Ret 0.025% Gel', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">A-Ret 0.025% Gel is a form of vitamin A that is used to treat acne which appears as spots or pimples on your face, chest or back. It also helps to smooth rough facial skin and to reduce fine wrinkles on the skin. A-Ret 0.025% Gel reduces excessive oil production of the skin. Ideally, a pinpoint application at nighttime is recommended for the duration prescribed by your doctor. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF A-RET GEL</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Acne</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">A-Ret 0.025% Gel is a form of vitamin A. It helps treat acne by clearing skin pores and preventing spots or pimples from appearing. It usually takes several weeks to have a noticeable effect so keep using it even if it appears not to be working. Sometimes acne may get worse before it gets better, however, with proper use, your skin will get clearer. </div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_10_17_22.jpg', '', 84.00, NULL, 'Tube of 20 gm', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:47:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(444, 1, 'A Ret HC Cream', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">A Ret HC Cream is a prescription medicine having a combination of medicines that is used to treat melasma. It helps in quick skin renewal. It provides relief from redness, swelling and itching.<br>A Ret HC Cream should be used in the dose and duration as advised by your doctor. Wash your hands before using this medicine. It is advised to check the label for directions before use. It is for external use only.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF A RET HC CREAM</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Melasma</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Melasma is a common skin problem that causes dark, discolored patches on your skin primarily on the face. It frequently occurs during pregnancy and menopause. A Ret HC Cream helps to lighten these dark patches by reducing the production of melanin (natural skin pigment). It lightens skin color and gives a smoother-looking skin. A Ret HC Cream also reduces any swelling, redness and itchiness especially if you have a sensitive skin. This helps boost your self-esteem and confidence as your appearance changes. Keep using it for as long as it is prescribed to get the full benefits.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_10_40_26.jpg', '', 139.00, NULL, 'Tube of 15 gm', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:46:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(445, 1, 'Arg 9 Sachet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__product-description___1PfGf\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Arg 9 Granules</span> is prescribed during pregnancy as it helps prevent anemia and helps in proper growth of the fetus. It prevents birth defects. It is used in the formation of connective tissues.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>L-Arginine helps to improve the health and growth of the fetus in pregnant women with pre-eclampsia</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Proanthocyanidinis a type of flavonoid and antioxidant that helps in stabilizing collagen within body and also helps in maintenance of elastin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Used in formation of connective tissue</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Prevents nutritional deficiency and promotes fetal growth</li></ul></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_10_01_33.jfif', '', 38.80, NULL, '1 PACKET OF 5 GM GRANULES', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:45:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(446, 1, 'Argihope Plus Liquid', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Argihope Plus Liquid contains L- Arginine, Vitamin C, Zinc Sulphate Monohydrate, Pyridoxine HCl, Methylcobalamin, Folic Acid, and Vitamin E as active ingredients. One solution for multiple pregnancy complications.<br><br>Key benefits/uses of Argihope Plus Liquid:<br>- L- Arginine stimulates the release of insulin, growth hormones as well as other substances in the body<br>- Multivitamins are best dietary supplements to provide essential nutrients<br>- Vitamin E and C decrease the chances of birth defects/stillbirth<br>- Zinc is an essential supplement for cell growth and DNA of the baby<br>- Also, used as a dietary supplement for pregnant women<br>- Increases blood circulation<br>- Prevents intrauterine growth retardation<br>- Used for immunity building<br>- The formulation is sugar-free<br><br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_10_42_36.jpg', '', 299.00, NULL, '1 Bottle of 100 ml', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:45:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(447, 1, 'Argipreg Sachet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__product-description___1PfGf\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify;\">Argipreg Sachet contains L- Arginine, and Proanthocyanidin as the active ingredients.<br>- Acts as an antioxidant and increases body’s immunity<br>- Also removes harmful radicals from cells and sugar-free<br><br>Key benefits/uses of Argipreg Sachet:<br>- L- Arginine relaxes blood vessels in blood pressure patients and strengthens immunity<br>- Proanthocyanidins (PAs), also known as condensed tannins, are very powerful antioxidants and removes harmful free oxygen radicals from cells. They help in promoting youthful skin, cell health, elasticity, and flexibility&nbsp;<br>- The Proanthocyanidins also protects the body from UV rays damage, improve flexibility in joints, arteries, and body tissues<br>- Also improves blood circulation by strengthening capillaries, arteries, and veins<br></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_10_36_41.jpg', '', 41.00, NULL, '1 Sachet of 6.5 gm granules', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:44:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
