(448, 1, 'Argiprime Sugar Free Sachet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__product-description___1PfGf\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Argiprime for Oral Solution Sugar Free Sachet</span> is a combination of ingredients which increases placental circulation, pre-term labor, prevent growth retardation, erectile dysfunction and prevent early miscarriage.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>L-arginine and Proanthocyanidins, a combination of nutritional supplement</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It increases placental circulation, preterm labor, prevent growth retardation, erectile dysfunction and prevent early miscarriage</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It is used for promotion of cardiovascular health</li></ul></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_10_52_45.jpg', '', 36.00, NULL, '1 Sachet of 5 gm granules', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:42:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(450, 1, 'Aricep 10 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aricep 10 Tablet is used to treat mild to moderate dementia in Alzheimer’s disease, a progressive illness that gradually affects memory and thinking. It does not cure this illness but may help improve memory, awareness, and other symptoms.<br></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARICEP TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Alzheimer\'s disease</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">In people with Alzheimer’s disease, certain nerve cells die in the brain. This results in lower levels of a chemical called acetylcholine which helps nerve cells to communicate with each other. This leads to symptoms of dementia such as memory loss, confusion, disorientation, problems with speech and language, and personality changes. Aricep 10 Tablet increases the amount of acetylcholine and helps brain cells to communicate. It can, therefore, improve some of the symptoms such as memory, awareness, and the ability to carry out daily functions for a time. However, it is not a cure. You should use the medicine exactly as prescribed.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_10_38_56.jpg', '', 162.75, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:35:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(451, 1, 'Aricep 5 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aricep 5 Tablet is used to treat mild to moderate dementia in Alzheimer’s disease, a progressive illness that gradually affects memory and thinking. It does not cure this illness but may help improve memory, awareness, and other symptoms.<br></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARICEP TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Alzheimer\'s disease</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">In people with Alzheimer’s disease, certain nerve cells die in the brain. This results in lower levels of a chemical called acetylcholine which helps nerve cells to communicate with each other. This leads to symptoms of dementia such as memory loss, confusion, disorientation, problems with speech and language, and personality changes. Aricep 5 Tablet increases the amount of acetylcholine and helps brain cells to communicate. It can, therefore, improve some of the symptoms such as memory, awareness, and the ability to carry out daily functions for a time. However, it is not a cure. You should use the medicine exactly as prescribed. It can take several weeks for your symptoms to improve; so keep using the medicine even if you do not think it is working</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611050251.jpg', '', 114.00, NULL, 'STRIP OF 10 TABLETS', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:41:26', '2021-01-19 15:27:31'),
(453, 1, 'Aripra MT 10mg Tablet', '<div><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aripra MT 10mg Tablet is an antipsychotic medicine. It is used in the treatment of schizophrenia (a mental disorder that can result in hallucinations or delusions and also adversely affects a person’s ability to think and behave) and mania. It can also be used to treat depression and bipolar disorders.Aripra MT 10mg Tablet may be taken with or without food, preferably in the morning. However, it is advised to take it at the same time each day as this helps to maintain a consistent level of medicine in the body. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARIPRA MT TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Schizophrenia</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Schizophrenia is a mental disorder in which a person’s thinking ability, feelings and behavior become abnormal. Aripra MT 10mg Tablet helps restore the chemical imbalances in the brain that are responsible for such changes. It improves thoughts, behavior and enhances the quality of life.</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Mania</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Mania means extremely excited or elevated mood. Aripra MT 10mg Tablet helps calm the mood and relax the nerves. This stabilises the mood and prevents the symptoms of mania from recurring again. Taking Aripra MT 10mg Tablet will ensure that you have a better social life and are able to do daily activities more comfortably.</span></div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_11_07_08.jpg', '', 190.90, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:41:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(454, 1, 'Arip MT 5 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arip MT 5 Tablet is an antipsychotic medicine. It is used in the treatment of schizophrenia (a mental disorder that can result in hallucinations or delusions and also adversely affects a person’s ability to think and behave) and mania. It can also be used to treat depression and bipolar disorders.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARIP MT TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Schizophrenia</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Schizophrenia is a mental disorder in which a person’s thinking ability, feelings and behavior become abnormal. Arip MT 5 Tablet helps restore the chemical imbalances in the brain that are responsible for such changes. It improves thoughts, behavior and enhances the quality of life.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); text-transform: capitalize;\">&nbsp;In Mania&nbsp;</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Mania means extremely excited or elevated mood. Arip MT 5 Tablet helps calm the mood and relax the nerves. This stabilises the mood and prevents the symptoms of mania from recurring again. Taking Arip MT 5 Tablet will ensure that you have a better social life and are able to do daily activities more comfortably.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611050552.jpg', '', 110.15, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:39:53', '2021-01-19 15:32:32'),
(455, 1, 'Aristozyme Capsule', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Aristozyme Capsule contains 50mg diastase and 10mg pepsin.<br>Diastase is an enzyme that will convert starches into maltose, which can then be converted into glucose for energy. Pepsin is also included to break down proteins into small peptides. This works in the stomach to improve how well proteins are digested after eating. Aristozyme capsules are used to assist in the digestion of acids in the body. Aristozyme capsule may also be used to treat flatulence, dyspepsia and the sour feelings that might develop in one\'s stomach on occasion. It may also improve a person\'s appetite in some cases.<br><br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_11_09_17.jpg', '', 61.50, NULL, '10 Capsules in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:40:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(456, 1, 'Aristozyme liquid', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Aristozyme liquid contains Fungal diastase and Pepsin. Aristozyme liquid provides relief from gas, heartburn & indigestion.<br>Fungal Diastase is a digestive Enzyme that helps in Carbohydrate Digestion. It helps in digestion of starch, carbohydrates, fats & Proteins. Fungal diastase is used as digestive aid in case of loss of appetite due to chronic illness, stomach fullness and indigestion.<br>Pepsin is an enzyme that breaks down proteins into smaller peptides (that is, a protease). It is produced in the stomach and is one of the main digestive enzymes in the digestive systems of humans and many other animals, where it helps digest the proteins in food. Pepsin exhibits excellent digestion power. Pepsin help in digestive disturbance<br> </div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_12_34_43.jpg', '', 104.00, NULL, '1 BOTTLE OF 200 ML LIQUID', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:31:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(457, 14, 'Himalaya Arjuna Capsule', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Himalaya Arjuna Capsule</span> promotes a healthy cardiovascular system. Arjuna helps to provide relief in angina, atherosclerosis, and symptoms of heart failure. Arjuna also promotes healthy liver, kidney, and digestive functions. In addition to this, it refreshes mind and reduces stress in the body.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps to strengthen and maintain the integrity of gastric mucosa (the lining of the stomach)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Arjuna bark works on an increasing the levels of superoxide dismutase, catalase and glutathione levels</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps to guard the body against oxidative stress</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Assists in achieving healthy arterial blood flow and healthy muscular contractions</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps to guard the heart from chronic high blood pressure</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Beneficial in the case of angina, atherosclerosis, and symptoms of heart failure</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It helps to manage the cholesterol level in the body</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Contains antioxidant and antibacterial properties</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611050897.jpg', '', 165.00, NULL, 'Bottle of 60 Capsules', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:38:41', '2021-01-19 15:38:17'),
(458, 14, 'Dabur Arjunarishta Liquid', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Dabur Arjunarishta</span>&nbsp;is nutritional support for a healthy heart function. It&nbsp;is natural and gives relieves heart and respiratory problems. The main herb used in Arjunarishta is Arjuna which is according to Ayurveda the herb of choice for cardiovascular health. It is indicated in Heart disorders such as blocked arteries, angina, enlarged heart ischemia. Moreover, Arjunarishta is useful in the treatment of chest injury, Anorexia and Irregular Heart Beat. It is effective in the treatment of chronic respiratory diseases, cough, and throat related problems.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps to improve the Heart health</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Used in the treatment of Irregular heart beat and Chest injury</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Provides relief in the case of insomnia</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps to regulate blood pressure and cholesterol level</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps to clean the intestine and relieves general weakness</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps to improve the stomach health</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/190221_11_05_34.jpg', '', 145.00, NULL, 'Bottle of 200 ml Liquid', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:37:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(459, 1, 'Arkamin Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arkamin Tablet is a medicine used in the treatment of hypertension (high blood pressure). It lowers the blood pressure by relaxing the blood vessels. Lowering the blood pressure helps to prevent future stroke and heart attack.<br>Arkamin Tablet is also used to prevent migraine and hot flushes in women during menopause. This medicine can be taken with or without food but it is better to take it at the same time every day. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARKAMIN TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arkamin Tablet works by relaxing the blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This lowers your blood pressure and reduces your risk of having a stroke, a heart attack, or kidney problems in the future. You do not usually feel any direct benefit from taking this medicine, but it works in the long term to keep you well. You should take it regularly as prescribed for this medicine to be most effective.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611051094.jpg', '', 60.10, NULL, '30 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:32:20', '2021-01-19 15:41:34'),
(460, 1, 'Ark Gel', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Ark Gel is used to relieve pain associated with muscle or joint injuries such as sprains, strains, or sports injuries. It also relieves pain from rheumatoid arthritis, osteoarthritis etc. It contains Diclofenac, Capsaicin, Methyl Salicylate and Menthol.<br>Role of key ingredients:<br>Diclofenac, which is used to treat acute muscular pain. Diclofenac belongs to the class of medications known as nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs (NSAIDs). It works by reducing pain, swelling, and inflammation by inhibiting the synthesis of prostaglandins.<br>Capsaicin is derived from capsicum. Capsaicin help in relieve from pain and inflammation. It stimulates the release of a compound involved in communicating pain between the nerves in the spinal cord and other parts of the body thus decreases the intensity of pain signals in the body.<br>Methyl Salicylate reduces inflammation.<br>Menthol is a compound with analgesic effects. Menthol targets kappa-opioid receptors in the brain, resulting in temporary relief from minor pain.<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611051230.jpg', '', 110.00, NULL, 'Tube of 30 gm gel', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:36:16', '2021-01-19 15:43:50'),
(462, 1, 'Arpizol 10 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arpizol 10 Tablet is an antipsychotic medicine. It is used in the treatment of schizophrenia (a mental disorder that can result in hallucinations or delusions and also adversely affects a person’s ability to think and behave) and mania. It can also be used to treat depression and bipolar disorders.Arpizol 10 Tablet may be taken with or without food, preferably in the morning. However, it is advised to take it at the same time each day as this helps to maintain a consistent level of medicine in the body. <br><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARPIZOL TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Schizophrenia</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Schizophrenia is a mental disorder in which a person’s thinking ability, feelings and behavior become abnormal. Arpizol 10 Tablet helps restore the chemical imbalances in the brain that are responsible for such changes. It improves thoughts, behavior and enhances the quality of life.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Mania</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Mania means extremely excited or elevated mood. Arpizol 10 Tablet helps calm the mood and relax the nerves. This stabilises the mood and prevents the symptoms of mania from recurring again. </div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611051747.jpg', '', 118.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:32:36', '2021-01-19 15:52:27'),
