(464, 1, 'Arpizol 5 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arpizol 5 Tablet is an antipsychotic medicine. It is used in the treatment of schizophrenia (a mental disorder that can result in hallucinations or delusions and also adversely affects a person’s ability to think and behave) and mania. It can also be used to treat depression and bipolar disorders.Arpizol 5 Tablet may be taken with or without food, preferably in the morning. However, it is advised to take it at the same time each day as this helps to maintain a consistent level of medicine in the body.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARPIZOL TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Schizophrenia\r\nMania\r\nBENEFITS OF ARPIZOL TAB</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">In Schizophrenia</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Schizophrenia is a mental disorder in which a person’s thinking ability, feelings and behavior become abnormal. Arpizol 5 Tablet helps restore the chemical imbalances in the brai