(484, 1, 'Arvast Gold 20 Capsule', '<h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arvast Gold 20 Capsule is used for prevention of heart attack. It is a combination of medicines that prevent clot formation in the blood vessels. It also helps to reduce increased cholesterol and triglycerides levels.<br>Arvast Gold 20 Capsule is used for prevention of heart attack. It is a combination of medicines that prevents clot formation in the blood vessels. It also helps to reduce increased cholesterol and triglycerides levels.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ARVAST GOLD CAPSULE</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Heart attack</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Arvast Gold 20 Capsule is a combination medicine that is used to prevent heart attack. It contains Rosuvastatin that works by reducing the amount of “bad” cholesterol (LDL) and raising the amount of “good” cholesterol (HDL) in your blood. High levels of cholesterol can cause your blood vessels to narrow (atherosclerosis). Lowering the amount of cholesterol reduces the chances of heart diseases and helps you remain healthier for longer.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/150321_12_07_01.jpg', '', 188.38, NULL, '10 Capsules in 1 Strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 12:01:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(485, 1, 'Asar 40 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asar 40 Tablet is a medicine used to treat high blood pressure and heart failure. Lowering blood pressure helps to prevent future heart attack and stroke. This medicine is also effective in preserving kidney function in patients with diabetes.&nbsp;<br>Asar 40 Tablet can be prescribed either alone or in combination with other medicines.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASAR TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asar 40 Tablet lowers blood pressure by relaxing blood vessels and making it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. It must be taken regularly as prescribed to be effective.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Heart failure</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Heart failure means your heart is weak and cannot pump enough blood to your lungs and the rest of your body. The most common symptoms are breathlessness, tiredness, and swelling in your legs, ankles, abdomen, and other parts of your body. Asar 40 Tablet lowers your blood pressure which makes it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body and is, therefore, an effective treatment for heart failure.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of heart attack and stroke</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asar 40 Tablet lowers your blood pressure and makes it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. If your blood pressure is controlled you are less at risk of having a heart attack or stroke. Keep taking this medicine regularly.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/040321_07_29_58.jpg', '', 91.00, NULL, '1X10', NULL, 1, '2021-03-04 07:58:29', '2021-01-19 16:14:48'),
(486, 1, 'Ascabiol Emulsion', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascabiol Emulsion is a combination medicine that is used to treat scabies. It kills the tiny insects (mites) and their eggs. It also kills head lices.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASCABIOL SOLUTION</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Scabies</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Scabies is a condition caused by tiny insects called mites that infest and irritate your skin. Ascabiol Emulsion kills the mites and their eggs present on the skin. This gives relief from itching, swelling and redness. Ascabiol Emulsion also helps kill head lices and their eggs, therbey giving you relief from itching and irritation caused by lice. It is normally effective in one or two applications however complete the course of treatment for better results.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611053305.jpg', '', 99.25, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 12:03:05', '2021-01-19 16:18:25'),
(487, 1, 'Ascazin 220mg Capsule', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Ascazin tablet is an advanced formula of high concentration of Zinc. Zinc has been found to be very important for boosting up immunity. Azcazin tablets can be used a nutritional supplement and aids in the absorption of calcium by the body as well.<br> <br>Azcazin can be used in treating all immune deficiency disorders. Azcazin is the best nutritional support in cardiac, diabetic, tubercular and rheumatic patients as well as those suffering from acute and chronic diseases. Azcazin Tablets recommended as a dietary supplement beneficial in the following conditions:<br>To reduce recovery time in respiratory tract infection, diarrhea and wound and injury.<br> <br>Use under Medical supervision.<br> </div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/150321_12_55_05.jpg', '', 65.20, NULL, '10 Capsules in 1 Strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 12:05:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(489, 1, 'Ascoril D Plus Syrup Sugar Free', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril D Plus Syrup Sugar Free is a combination medicine used in the treatment of dry cough. It relieves allergic symptoms such as sneezing, runny nose, watery eyes, and throat irritation. It also provides relief from congestion or stuffiness in the nose.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASCORIL D PLUS SYRUP</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Dry cough</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">A dry cough, also known as non-productive cough, is a cough where no phlegm or mucus is produced. This is irritating, usually associated with a tickly throat and may be caused due to cold, flu, allergies or throat irritants. Ascoril D Plus Syrup Sugar Free suppresses dry, hacking coughs. It will also relieve allergy symptoms like watery eyes, sneezing, runny nose or throat irritation.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/150321_12_43_12.jpg', '', 113.00, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 12:12:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(490, 1, 'Ascoril LS Drops', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><br></h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril LS Drops comprises three active ingredients that together help treat wet cough (cough with mucus), acute sore throat, asthma, and chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD) in children. It also relieves throat irritation, clears congestion, and enables easy breathing in your child.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASCORIL LS DROPS&nbsp;</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril LS Drops helps gently soothe and relieve your child’s cough. It loosens thick mucus thereby making it easier to cough out. This makes breathing easy and reduces the frequency of coughing. Along with medications, drinking lukewarm water and gargling with warm salt water may also help ease symptoms for your child.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Acute Sore throat</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Sore throat refers to pain and discomfort in the throat that is usually seen in bacterial or viral infections. Ascoril LS Drops works quite quickly to reduce the pain and discomfort for your child. It helps soothe the irritated throat and speeds up the recovery process.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Asthma</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril LS Drops is a combination medicine that relaxes the muscles of your child’s airways thereby making it easier for the air to get in and out. It helps prevent symptoms such as wheezing, coughing, and shortness of breath.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril LS Drops is a combination of medicines that helps the airways in the lungs stay open. It will relieve symptoms such as tightness in the chest, shortness of breath, wheezing, and coughing.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/150321_12_55_53.jpg', '', 58.00, NULL, '15 ml in 1 Bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 12:53:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(491, 1, 'Ascoril LS Junior Syrup', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril LS Junior Syrup is a combination medicine used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It thins mucus in the nose, windpipe and lungs, making it easier to cough out. It also provides relief from runny nose, sneezing, itching, and watery eyes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASCORIL LS SYRUP</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril LS Junior Syrup gives relief from cough with mucus. It helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes breathing easy and reduces the frequency of coughing. Ascoril LS Junior Syrup will also relieve allergy symptoms like watery eyes, sneezing, runny nose or throat irritation.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/150321_13_04_07.png', '', 75.00, NULL, '60 ml in 1 Bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 13:07:04', '2021-01-19 16:27:11'),
(492, 1, 'Ascoril LS Syrup', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril LS Syrup is a combination medicine used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It thins mucus in the nose, windpipe and lungs, making it easier to cough out. It also provides relief from runny nose, sneezing, itching, and watery eyes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASCORIL LS SYRUP</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril LS Syrup gives relief from cough with mucus. It helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes breathing easy and reduces the frequency of coughing. Ascoril LS Syrup will also relieve allergy symptoms like watery eyes, sneezing, runny nose or throat irritation.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/150321_13_17_11.jpg', '', 98.50, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 13:11:17', '2021-01-19 16:28:54'),
(493, 1, 'Ascoril Plus Expectorant', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril Plus Expectorant is used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It thins mucus in the nose, windpipe and lungs, making it easier to cough out. It also provides relief from runny nose, sneezing, itching, and watery eyes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASCORIL PLUS EXPECTORANT</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril Plus Expectorant helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes it easier for air to move in and out. It will relieve symptoms such as tightness in your chest, shortness of breath, wheezing and coughing and help you carry out your daily activities more easily. This medicine is safe and effective. It usually starts to work within a few minutes and the effects can last up to several hours.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/150321_13_41_19.jpg', '', 115.00, NULL, '120 ml in 1 Bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-15 13:20:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(494, 1, 'Ascoril SF Expectorant', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril SF Expectorant is used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It thins mucus in the nose, windpipe and lungs, making it easier to cough out. It also provides relief from runny nose, sneezing, itching, and watery eyes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASCORIL SF EXPECTORANT</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Ascoril SF Expectorant helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes it easier for air to move in and out. It will relieve symptoms such as tightness in your chest, shortness of breath, wheezing and coughing.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611054147.jpg', '', 108.00, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 08:27:42', '2021-01-19 16:32:27'),
(496, 14, 'Dabur Ashokarishta', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Dabur Ashokarishta</span>&nbsp;is especially helpful in reducing menstrual cramps and period pains in women. It is an ayurvedic health tonic beneficial for women in difficulties during their menstrual days. Ashokarishta contains the goodness of medicinal plants like Ashoka, Dhataki, Musta, Haritaki and Amlaki, which have anti-inflammatory and rejuvenating properties.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Ashoka</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Dhataki</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Musta</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Haritaki</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Amlaki</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Ashoka is known to have analgesic and anti-inflammatory properties and has a beneficial effect on the skin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Dhataki has healing properties</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Musta has appetizing and anti-inflammatory properties</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Haritaki &amp; Amlaki have rejuvenating, antioxidant and immune-modulatory properties and are beneficial in general weakness</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:<br></span>(Adults): 1 to 2 tablespoonful (15 to 30ml) with equal quantity of water after meals or as directed by the physician.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611054417.jpg', '', 133.00, NULL, '1 Bottle of 680 ml Syrup', NULL, 1, '2021-03-04 08:01:36', '2021-01-19 16:36:57'),
(499, 1, 'Asomex 2.5 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 2.5 Tablet is a medicine used to treat high blood pressure (hypertension) and to prevent angina (heart-related chest pain). It is a calcium channel blocker which helps to lower blood pressure and reduce the workload of the heart. This helps prevent heart attacks and strokes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASOMEX TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 2.5 Tablet is a calcium channel blocker. It works by relaxing the blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This lowers your blood pressure and reduces your risk of having a stroke, a heart attack, or kidney problems in the future.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of Angina (heart-related chest pain)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 2.5 Tablet belongs to a class of medicines known as a calcium channel blockers. It works by relaxing blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This means that more oxygen gets to your heart and reduces the risk of getting chest pain (angina). This medicine should not be used to treat chest pain which is already happening. It is used to prevent or reduce the frequency of angina attacks.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of Heart attack</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 2.5 Tablet helps lower your blood pressure and make it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. This reduces the chances of you having a heart attack. It can also reduce the risk of dying if it is given immediately after a heart attack. This medicine needs to be taken regularly to be effective.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of Stroke</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 2.5 Tablet reduces the risk of future strokes. It helps lower your blood pressure and make it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. This reduces the chances of you having a stroke.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611056724.jpg', '', 91.20, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 08:47:43', '2021-01-19 17:15:24'),
(500, 1, 'Asomex 5 Tablet', '<h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 5 Tablet is a medicine used to treat high blood pressure (hypertension) and to prevent angina (heart-related chest pain). It is a calcium channel blocker which helps to lower blood pressure and reduce the workload of the heart. This helps prevent heart attacks and strokes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASOMEX TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 5 Tablet is a calcium channel blocker. It works by relaxing the blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This lowers your blood pressure and reduces your risk of having a stroke, a heart attack, or kidney problems in the future.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of Angina (heart-related chest pain)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 5 Tablet belongs to a class of medicines known as a calcium channel blockers. It works by relaxing blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This means that more oxygen gets to your heart and reduces the risk of getting chest pain (angina). This medicine should not be used to treat chest pain which is already happening. It is used to prevent or reduce the frequency of angina attacks.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of Heart attack</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 5 Tablet helps lower your blood pressure and make it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. This reduces the chances of you having a heart attack. It can also reduce the risk of dying if it is given immediately after a heart attack. This medicine needs to be taken regularly to be effective.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of Stroke</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex 5 Tablet reduces the risk of future strokes. It helps lower your blood pressure and make it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. This reduces the chances of you having a stroke.&nbsp;</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611054840.jpg', '', 142.15, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 08:53:09', '2021-01-19 16:44:00');
INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `category_id`, `product_name`, `product_description`, `product_thumbnail`, `product_alt`, `price`, `discount_price`, `product_size`, `prescription_required`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(501, 1, 'Asomex-AT Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex-AT Tablet is used to treat hypertension (high blood pressure). This is a combination of two medicines that controls blood pressure when a single medication is not effective. It helps to lower high blood pressure and thus reduces the chances of future heart attack and stroke.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASOMEX-AT TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex-AT Tablet is a combination medicine that contains two active ingredients, Amlodipine and Atenolol. Both of the medicines in this combination work to lower blood pressure but in different ways. Together they help to relax blood vessels, reduce heart rate and make it easier for your heart to pump blood around your body. This lowers blood pressure.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_08_28_58.jpg', '', 158.70, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 08:58:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(502, 1, 'Asomex-D Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex-D Tablet is a combination medicine used in the treatment of hypertension (high blood pressure). It also helps to reduce the risk of stroke and heart attack. Asomex-D Tablet is a combination medicine used in the treatment of hypertension (high blood pressure). It also helps to reduce the risk of stroke and heart attack. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASOMEX-D TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex-D Tablet relaxes the blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. It also eliminates excess water from the body and increases urine output. This maintains balance of electrolytes (like potassium), lowers your blood pressure and reduces your risk of having a stroke, a heart attack, or kidney problems in the future. </div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_09_11_52.jpg', '', 114.80, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 09:52:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(503, 1, 'Asomex-OH Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex-OH Tablet is a combination of medicines used to treat hypertension (high blood pressure) when a single medication is not effective. It helps to lower high blood pressure thus reduces chances of future heart attack and stroke.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASOMEX-OH TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex-OH Tablet relaxes the blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. It also eliminates excess water from the body and increases urine output. This lowers your blood pressure and reduces your risk of having a stroke, a heart attack, or kidney problems in the future.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611055161.jpg', '', 142.45, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 09:54:13', '2021-01-19 16:49:21'),
(504, 1, 'Asomex-TM Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex-TM Tablet is a combination medicine used in the treatment of hypertension (high blood pressure). It works by relaxing the blood vessels and making the heart more efficient at pumping blood throughout the body.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASOMEX-TM TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asomex-TM Tablet relaxes the blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This lowers your blood pressure and reduces your risk of having a stroke, a heart attack, or kidney problems in the future.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_09_11_56.jpg', '', 180.20, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 09:56:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(505, 1, 'Aspifast Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">- Aspifast Tablet consists of Chondroitin Sulfate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Collagen peptide, Methylsulfonylmethane, Rosehip extract, Vitamin C as active ingredients.<br><br>Key benefits/UsesAspifast Tablet:<br>- Chondroitin sulfate is recommended as a therapeutic intervention in the multimodal approach to osteoarthritis management<br>- Methylsulfonylmethane is a small sulfur containing molecule related to DSMO which is used for its antioxidative and anti- inflammatory properties.<br>- Rosehip extract is believed to ease joint inflammation and prevent joint damage.<br>- Vitamin Cis used to help growth and good health.<br><br>Direction for use/Dosage:<br>- As directed by the physician.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_09_37_59.jpg', '', 375.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 09:59:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(506, 1, 'Aspira MR 60mg/4mg Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aspira MR 60mg/4mg Tablet is a combination of two medicines used in the treatment of pain due to muscle spasm. It improves the movement of muscles and provides relief from pain and discomfort associated with muscle spasms.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASPIRA MR TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Pain due to muscle spasm</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aspira MR 60mg/4mg Tablet is a combination medicine that contains a painkiller as well as a muscle relaxant. It is used to relieve pain, inflammation, and swelling in conditions that affect muscles. Also, it effectively relieves muscle stiffness or spasm, thereby improving muscle movement. It works by blocking chemical messengers in the brai that tell us we have pain.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_10_36_01.jpg', '', 191.90, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:01:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(507, 1, 'Aspira-S Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aspira-S Tablet is a combination medicine used to relieve pain and swelling in various conditions like muscle pain, joint pain and postoperative pain. Thus, it effectively alleviates pain and inflammation in conditions like rheumatoid arthritis, ankylosing spondylitis and osteoarthritis.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASPIRA-S TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Pain relief</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aspira-S Tablet is a combination medicine that is used for short term relief of pain, inflammation, and swelling in conditions that affect joints and muscles. It works by blocking chemical messengers in the brain that tell us we have pain. It can help relieve pain in conditions like rheumatoid arthritis and osteoarthritis. Along with painkillers, this medicine also contains an active ingredient called Serratiopeptidase, which is an enzyme that promotes the overall healing process and speeds up recovery.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_10_08_05.png', '', 82.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:05:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(508, 1, 'Aspira 100mg/500mg Tablet', '<h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aspira 100mg/500mg Tablet is a pain relieving medicine. It is used to reduce pain and inflammation in conditions like rheumatoid arthritis, ankylosing spondylitis, and osteoarthritis. It may also be used to relieve muscle pain, back pain, toothache, or pain in the ear and throat.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Nunito, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">USES OF ASPIRA TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: Nunito, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">In Pain relief</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Aspira 100mg/500mg Tablet is a combination of two medicines that belong to a group of medicines called nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs (NSAIDs). It is used for short term relief of pain, inflammation, and swelling in conditions that affect joints and muscles. It works by blocking chemical messengers that are responsible for causing the pain sensation. It can help relieve pain in conditions like rheumatoid arthritis and osteoarthritis.</div></div></div></div></div></h2>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_10_18_07.png', '', 37.40, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:07:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(511, 1, 'Asprito 10 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asprito 10 Tablet is an antipsychotic medicine. It is used in the treatment of schizophrenia (a mental disorder that can result in hallucinations or delusions and also adversely affects a person’s ability to think and behave) and mania. It can also be used to treat depression and bipolar disorders.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASPRITO TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Schizophrenia</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Schizophrenia is a mental disorder in which a person’s thinking ability, feelings and behavior become abnormal. Asprito 10 Tablet helps restore the chemical imbalances in the brain that are responsible for such changes. It improves thoughts, behavior.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Mania</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Mania means extremely excited or elevated mood. Asprito 10 Tablet helps calm the mood and relax the nerves. This stabilises the mood and prevents the symptoms of mania from recurring again.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611055532.jpg', '', 131.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:11:08', '2021-01-19 16:55:32'),
(512, 1, 'Asprito 15 Tablet', '<h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asprito 15 Tablet is an antipsychotic medicine. It is used in the treatment of schizophrenia (a mental disorder that can result in hallucinations or delusions and also adversely affects a person’s ability to think and behave) and mania. It can also be used to treat depression and bipolar disorders.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASPRITO TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Schizophrenia</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Schizophrenia is a mental disorder in which a person’s thinking ability, feelings and behavior become abnormal. Asprito 15 Tablet helps restore the chemical imbalances in the brain that are responsible for such changes. It improves thoughts, behavior.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Mania</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Mania means extremely excited or elevated mood. Asprito 15 Tablet helps calm the mood and relax the nerves. This stabilises the mood and prevents the symptoms of mania from recurring again.&nbsp;</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611055590.jpg', '', 183.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:12:10', '2021-01-19 16:56:30'),
