ted or elevated mood. Asprito 20 Tablet helps calm the mood and relax the nerves. This stabilises the mood and prevents the symptoms of mania from recurring again.&nbsp;</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611055662.jpg', '', 183.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:13:03', '2021-01-19 16:57:42'),
(514, 1, 'Asprito 2 Tablet', '<h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asprito 2 Tablet is an antipsychotic medicine. It is used in the treatment of schizophrenia (a mental disorder that can result in hallucinations or delusions and also adversely affects a person’s ability to think and behave) and mania. It can also be used to treat depression and bipolar disorders.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASPRITO TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Schizophrenia</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Schizophrenia is a mental disorder in which a person’s thinking ability, feelings and behavior become abnormal. Asprito 2 Tablet helps restore the chemical imbalances in the brain that are responsible for such changes. It improves thoughts, behavior. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Mania</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Mania means extremely excited or elevated mood. Asprito 2 Tablet helps calm the mood and relax the nerves. This stabilises the mood and prevents the symptoms of mania from recurring again. </div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_10_12_28.jpg', '', 35.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:28:12', '2021-01-19 16:58:32'),
(515, 1, 'Assurans Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Assurans Tablet is a medicine used to treat high blood pressure in the blood vessels that supply the lungs (pulmonary arterial hypertension). It relieves breathlessness and improves exercise capacity in men and women. This slows down the progression of your illness.&nbsp;<br>Assurans Tablet belongs to a group of medicines known as phosphodiesterase type 5 (PDE 5) inhibitors.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASSURANS TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Pulmonary arterial hypertension (PAH)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Pulmonary arterial hypertension can cause shortness of breath, tiredness, dizziness, chest pain, and swelling in your ankles and legs. It is caused by the thickening of walls of the arteries that supply your lungs making it hard for blood to get through. Assurans Tablet belongs to a group of medicines called PDE5 inhibitors. It works by relaxing blood vessels and can help lower the blood pressure in the arteries of your lungs.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611055851.jpg', '', 309.00, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:19:48', '2021-01-19 17:00:51'),
(516, 1, 'Astelor 10mg Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Astelor 10mg Tablet belongs to a group of medicines called antihistamines. It is used in the treatment of various allergic conditions. It relieves symptoms like itching, swelling and rashes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTELOR TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Allergic conditions</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Astelor 10mg Tablet provides relief from symptoms such as blocked or runny nose, sneezing, and itchy or watery eyes. It can also give relief from allergic reactions after insect bites and symptoms of hives and eczema such as rash, swelling, itching, and irritation.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_10_48_22.jpg', '', 55.00, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:22:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(518, 1, 'Asthakind-DX Syrup Sugar Free', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind-DX Syrup Sugar Free is a combination medicine used in the treatment of dry cough. It relieves allergic symptoms such as sneezing, runny nose, watery eyes, and throat irritation. It also provides relief from congestion or stuffiness in the nose.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHAKIND-DX SYRUP</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Dry cough</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">A dry cough, also known as non-productive cough, is a cough where no phlegm or mucus is produced. This is irritating, usually associated with a tickly throat and may be caused due to cold, flu, allergies or throat irritants. Asthakind-DX Syrup Sugar Free suppresses dry, hacking coughs. It will also relieve allergy symptoms like watery eyes, sneezing, runny nose or throat irritation.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_10_35_27.jpg', '', 78.65, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:27:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(519, 1, 'Asthakind Expectorant Sugar Free', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind Expectorant Sugar Free is used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It thins mucus in the nose, windpipe and lungs, making it easier to cough out. It also provides relief from runny nose, sneezing, itching, and watery eyes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHAKIND EXPECTORANT</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind Expectorant Sugar Free helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes it easier for air to move in and out. It will relieve symptoms such as tightness in your chest, shortness of breath, wheezing and coughing.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611056138.jpg', '', 70.85, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:31:06', '2021-01-19 17:05:38'),
(520, 1, 'Asthakind-LS Expectorant Cola Sugar Free', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind-LS Expectorant Cola Sugar Free is a combination medicine used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It thins mucus in the nose, windpipe and lungs, making it easier to cough out. It also provides relief from runny nose, sneezing, itching, and watery eyes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHAKIND-LS EXPECTORANT</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind-LS Expectorant Cola Sugar Free gives relief from cough with mucus. It helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes breathing easy and reduces the frequency of coughing. Asthakind-LS Expectorant Cola Sugar Free will also relieve allergy symptoms like watery eyes, sneezing, runny nose or throat irritation. Along with medications, drink enough luke warm water and gargle with warm salt water to ease the symptoms.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_10_24_34.jpg', '', 75.00, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:34:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(521, 1, 'Asthakind-P Drops', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind-P Drops is used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It loosens and thins mucus in the nose, windpipe, and lungs. This makes it easier for you to cough it out. It also relaxes and widens the muscles in the airways making it easier for you to breathe.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHAKIND-P ORAL DROPS</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind-P Drops gives relief from cough with mucus. It helps to loosen thick mucus, reduce its stickiness and makes it easier to cough out. This makes breathing easy and reduces the frequency of coughing. Asthakind-P Drops will also relieve allergy symptoms like watery eyes, sneezing, runny nose or throat irritation. Along with medications, drink enough luke warm water and gargle with warm salt water to ease the symptoms.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_10_23_38.jpg', '', 60.50, NULL, '15 ml in 1 packet', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 10:38:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(523, 1, 'Asthakind Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind Tablet is used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It thins mucus in the nose, windpipe and lungs, making it easier to cough out. It also provides relief from runny nose, sneezing, itching, and watery eyes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHAKIND TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthakind Tablet helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes it easier for air to move in and out. It will relieve symptoms such as tightness in your chest, shortness of breath, wheezing and coughing.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/160321_11_13_25.png', '', 28.97, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 11:25:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(524, 1, 'Asthalin 2 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthalin 2 Tablet is used to relieve symptoms of asthma and chronic obstructive pulmonary diseases (COPD) such as coughing, wheezing, and breathlessness. It helps in relaxing the muscles of the air passages, thus widening it and making it easier to breathe.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHALIN TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment and prevention of Asthma</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthalin 2 Tablet can help prevent the onset of an asthma attack if it is taken before exercise or exposure to some “triggers”. These may include house dust, pollen, pets, and cigarette smoke. This medicine will allow you to exercise more freely without worrying about getting symptoms such as wheezing, coughing, and shortness of breath.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment and prevention of Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Bronchodilators like Asthalin 2 Tablet help the airways in your lungs stay open. They work by relaxing the muscles of these airways. This makes it easier for air to get in and out. It will relieve symptoms such as tightness in your chest, shortness of breath, wheezing and coughing.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611056488.jpg', '', 4.87, NULL, '30 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 11:27:22', '2021-01-19 17:11:28'),
(525, 1, 'Asthalin 4 Tablet', '<h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthalin 4 Tablet is used to relieve symptoms of asthma and chronic obstructive pulmonary diseases (COPD) such as coughing, wheezing, and breathlessness. It helps in relaxing the muscles of the air passages, thus widening it and making it easier to breathe.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHALIN TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment and prevention of Asthma</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthalin 4 Tablet can help prevent the onset of an asthma attack if it is taken before exercise or exposure to some “triggers”. These may include house dust, pollen, pets, and cigarette smoke. This medicine will allow you to exercise more freely without worrying about getting symptoms such as wheezing, coughing, and shortness of breath.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment and prevention of Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Bronchodilators like Asthalin 4 Tablet help the airways in your lungs stay open. They work by relaxing the muscles of these airways. This makes it easier for air to get in and out. It will relieve symptoms such as tightness in your chest, shortness of breath, wheezing and coughing.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611056539.jpg', '', 6.01, NULL, '30 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 11:28:14', '2021-01-19 17:12:19'),
(526, 1, 'Asthalin AX Syrup', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthalin AX Syrup is a combination medicine used in the treatment of cough with mucus. It thins mucus in the nose, windpipe and lungs, making it easier to cough out. It also provides relief from runny nose, sneezing, itching, and watery eyes.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHALIN AX SYRUP</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Cough with mucus</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthalin AX Syrup gives relief from cough with mucus. It helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes breathing easy and reduces the frequency of coughing. Asthalin AX Syrup will also relieve allergy symptoms like watery eyes, sneezing, runny nose or throat irritation. Along with medications, drink enough luke warm water and gargle with warm salt water to ease the symptoms.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611057020.jpg', '', 86.51, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 11:29:56', '2021-01-19 17:20:20'),
(527, 1, 'Asthalin 100mcg Inhaler', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthalin 100mcg Inhaler belongs to a group of medicines called fast-acting bronchodilators or “relievers”. It’s used to treat the symptoms of asthma and chronic obstructive pulmonary diseases (COPD) such as coughing, wheezing, and breathlessness.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ASTHALIN INHALER</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Asthma</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Asthalin 100mcg Inhaler can help prevent the onset of an asthma attack if it is taken before exercise or exposure to some “triggers”. These may include house dust, pollen, pets, and cigarette smoke. This medicine will allow you to exercise more freely without worrying about getting symptoms such as wheezing, coughing, and shortness of breath.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Bronchodilators like Asthalin 100mcg Inhaler help the airways in your lungs stay open. They work by relaxing the muscles of these airways. This makes it easier for air to get in and out. It will relieve symptoms such as tightness in your chest, shortness of breath, wheezing and coughing.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611057203.jpg', '', 141.75, NULL, '200 MDI in 1 packet', NULL, 1, '2021-03-16 11:32:19', '2021-01-19 17:23:23');
