(535, 1, 'Atarax Anti Itch Lotion', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Atarax Anti-Itch Lotion</span>&nbsp;is clinically proven lotion to soothe itchy, dry skin. It helps in soothing sensitive skin, while relieving itchy, dry skin and enhancing skin’s moisture barrier. It has a calming effect on the skin and reduces itchiness and inflammation.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Pramoxine hydrochloride</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Aloe vera gel</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Relieves itching and pain caused by minor skin irritation such as minor burns, cuts, sunburn, insect bites, cold sores and rashes from poison ivy, poison oak and poison sumac</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Soothes the chicken pox rash and allergic itches</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Effectively soothes the skin and relieves sensations of discomfort</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Apply a thin layer of the Atarax Anti-Itch lotion on the affected area by gently massaging the lotion untill it is absorbed</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Apply 2-3 times a day</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611058178.jpg', '', 333.00, NULL, '1 Bottle of 100 ml lotion', NULL, 1, '2021-03-17 06:47:02', '2021-01-19 17:39:38'),
(536, 1, 'Atarax Drops', '<h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Atarax Drops is used to treat anxiety and helps to get relaxed before or after surgery. It is also used to treat symptoms of skin allergy like itching, swelling, and rashes in conditions such as eczema, dermatitis, and psoriasis.<br></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">USES OF ATARAX SYRUP</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul class=\"DrugOverview__list___1HjxR DrugOverview__uses___1jmC3\" style=\"padding-left: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"padding-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Anxiety</span><br></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><div class=\"ShowMoreArray__tile___2mFZk\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div><div>Atarax Drops reduces the symptoms of excessive anxiety and worry that are triggered only at the time of stressful conditions that last for a shorter duration.&nbsp;</div></div><div class=\"ShowMoreArray__content___2OHDK\" style=\"position: relative; max-height: 5000px; transition: max-height 0.5s ease 0s, padding 0.1s ease 0s;\"><div class=\"ShowMoreArray__tile___2mFZk\" style=\"position: relative;\"><h3 class=\"DrugOverview__m-top-8___1rr5V\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(26, 26, 26); margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">In Treatment of Skin conditions with inflammation &amp; itching</h3><div>Atarax Drops is effective in treating skin conditions with inflammation and itching such as eczema, dermatitis and psoriasis. It works by reducing the actions of chemicals in the body that cause inflammation of the skin. When used correctly it is a safe and effective treatment. It reduces the redness, rash, pain or itchiness caused by your skin’s reaction to an irritant.</div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/040321_08_28_10.jpg', '', 52.50, NULL, '1 Bottle of 15 ml', NULL, 1, '2021-03-04 08:10:28', '2021-01-19 17:41:31'),
(537, 1, 'Atarax Syrup', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Atarax Syrup is used to treat anxiety and helps to get relaxed before or after surgery. It is also used to treat symptoms of skin allergy like itching, swelling, and rashes in conditions such as eczema, dermatitis, and psoriasis.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ATARAX SYRUP</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Anxiety</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Atarax Syrup reduces the symptoms of excessive anxiety and worry that are triggered only at the time of stressful conditions that last for a shorter duration. These could be job interviews, exams, stage performances, etc. It can effectively manage feelings of restlessness, tiredness, difficulty concentrating and feeling irritable.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Skin conditions with inflammation &amp; itching</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Atarax Syrup is effective in treating skin conditions with inflammation and itching such as eczema, dermatitis and psoriasis. It works by reducing the actions of chemicals in the body that cause inflammation of the skin. When used correctly it is a safe and effective treatment. It reduces the redness, rash, pain or itchiness caused by your skin’s reaction to an irritant.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611058353.jpg', '', 83.00, NULL, '100 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-17 06:50:51', '2021-01-19 17:42:33'),
(538, 1, 'Atchol 10mg Tablet', '<div id=\"np_tab1\" class=\"druginfo_cont druginfo-dv bottom-line active\" style=\"padding: 16px 0px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(21, 27, 57, 0.05); color: rgb(88, 89, 91); font-family: Lato; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px;\"><div class=\"col-md-12\" style=\"width: 727.236px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px;\"><div class=\"inner-content\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: LatoBold; letter-spacing: 0.25px; padding: 4px 0px; color: rgb(117, 112, 136);\">INTRODUCTION</h2><p>ATCHOL 10MG contains Atorvastatin, which belongs to a group of medicines called Statins. It is used to&nbsp;reduce high cholesterol levels in patients,&nbsp;including those who have certain inherited cholesterol disorders. Cholesterol gets builds up in your blood vessels leading to narrowing of blood vessels resulting in heart attack or stroke.&nbsp;ATCHOL 10MG is intended to reduce high cholesterol levels and is important to follow diet along with appropriate exercise, while taking medication. If you regularly drink grapefruit juice, talk to your doctor, since it may increase the amount of atorvastatin in the blood. Diabetic patients have to monitor their blood sugar more frequently while taking this medicine.</p><p>Before taking this medicine, it is better to let your doctor know if you are suffering from any heart, liver or kidney disease. Ask your doctor for advice before taking any medicine, if you are pregnant, or if you are trying to become pregnant or breast feeding. The common side effects of ATCHOL 10MG includes headache, nausea, constipation, indigestion, diarrhoea and cold-like symptoms. This medicine has to be taken regularly and exactly as prescribed by your doctor.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF ATCHOL TABLET</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In High cholesterol</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Atchol 10 Tablet belongs to a group of medicines called statins. It works by reducing the amount of “bad” cholesterol (LDL) and raising the amount of “good” cholesterol (HDL) in your blood. Lowering the amount of cholesterol reduces the chances of heart diseases and helps you remain healthier for longer.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Prevention of Heart attack</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">High levels of cholesterol can cause your blood vessels to narrow (atherosclerosis) and put you at risk of having a stroke or heart disease. Lowering the amount of this fat reduces the chances of this happening and helps you remain healthier for longer.</span></p></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/170321_06_35_56.jpg', '', 24.11, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-17 07:03:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
