(684, 3, 'Johnsons Baby Blossom Soap', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Johnsons Baby Blossom Soap</span> is specially made for babies. The soap is clinically proven to be safe and mild to use on babies. It nourishes your baby’s delicate skin by keeping it soft and healthy. It is paraben, alcohol and dye free and is mildly fragrant to suit every baby\'s skin.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sodium Palmate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sodium Palm Kernelate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Water</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Disodium EDTA</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Disodium Etidronate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sodium Chloride</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Mineral Oil</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Fragrance</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Glycerine</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Titanium Dioxide</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>C12- C15 Alkyl Benzoate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Dimethicone</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>stearoxytrimethylsilane</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Stearyl Alcohol</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Tocopheryl Acetate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Milk Protein</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>CI 26100</li></ul><br><span style=\"fon