(740, 15, 'Bellissa Acne Soap', '<h3 style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: \"Open Sans\";\">Benefits of Bellissa Acne Soap:</h3><ul style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: \"Open Sans\"; font-size: 13px;\"><li style=\"list-style: disc !important;\">Prevents and treats Acne</li><li style=\"list-style: disc !important;\">Fortified with natural and Synthetic oleo chemical based surfactants</li><li style=\"list-style: disc !important;\">Gentle cleanser with excellent moisturizers, emollients and natural skin nourishers</li><li style=\"list-style: disc !important;\">Contains Anti-bacterial, Anti-septic, Anti-microbial and anti-inflammatory properties</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: \"Open Sans\";\">How to Use:</h3><ul style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84); font-family: \"Open Sans\"; font-size: 13px;\"><li style=\"list-style: disc !important;\">Use Bellissa Acne Soap as a replacement for ordinary soap during bathing</li></ul>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/090321_11_30_05.jpg', '', 169.00, NULL, '1 box of 75 gm soap', NULL, 1, '2021-03-09 11:21:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(741, 15, 'Bellissa Lite Cream', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Bellissa Lite Cream contains Boswellin Super, White Ten, pTeroWhite, and Niacinamide as main active ingredients. Bellissa Lite Cream improves fairness to the skin, maintains an even skin tone, provides antioxidant support to the skin and nourishes skin to make it bright & radiant.<br><br>Key benefits/uses of Bellissa Lite Cream:<br>Role of active ingredients:<br>- Boswellin Super: Acts as the skin conditioner, leaves your skin soft and smooth.It helps in fading away acne, surgery marks, stretch marks and other types of scars from the skin, it also reduces wrinkles and fine lines by regenerating healthy skin<br>- pTeroWhite: Functions as a skin conditioning agent with skin lightening and antioxidant properties<br>- Niacinamide: Improves the appearance of enlarged pores, uneven skin tone, fine lines, dullness, and a weakened skin surface<br><br>Directions for use/Dosage:<br>- Apply twice daily or as directed by the physician<br>- Massage gently until the cream disappears<br><br>Indication:<br>- Hyperpigmentation of skin, melasma, dark spots, brown spots and uneven skin tone<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/090321_11_57_07.jpg', '', 399.00, NULL, '1 Tube of 20 gm Cream', NULL, 1, '2021-03-09 11:20:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(742, 15, 'Bellissa Soap', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Bellissa Soap is a non-irritant mild cleanser formulated with Soap Noodles, Garcinia Indica Seed Butter, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract, and Olive Extract.<br><br>Benefits of Key ingredients:<br>Olive Oil, enriched with Vitamin E, nourishes, protects and softens skin, preventing chafing. It has soothing properties, which keep baby’s skin healthy and soft.<br>Glycerin moisturizes the skin by pulling water out into the top layer of the skin thereby preventing it from becoming dry, scaly, rough, flaky and itchy. Glycerin is useful for people suffering from skin dryness and infections of skin as it can relieve the symptoms of these conditions to make the skin soft and smooth. <br>Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract contains anti-septic and anti-bacterial properties that protect the skin from bacterial infections. It helps to treat skin diseases and combats common skin conditions like acne, wrinkles and dry skin. Aloe vera is used for dry skin, wound healing and as an anti-aging product. It also lightens and brightens the skin tone.<br><br>Bellissa Soap is recommended for all age groups. It makes the skin soft, supple, well hydrated and improves skin tone.<br><br>Use under medical supervision</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/090321_11_37_01.jpg', '', 145.00, NULL, '1 box of 75 gm soap', NULL, 1, '2021-03-09 11:21:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
