(789, 1, 'Betadine Vaginal Pessaries', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Betadine Vaginal Pessaries is an antiseptic and disinfectant agent. It is used to prevent and treat infection in the vagina that causes itching, irritation, and soreness. It works by killing or preventing the growth of infectious microorganisms in the vagina.<br>Betadine Vaginal Pessaries is for external use only.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF BETADINE PESSARIES</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment and prevention of Vaginal Infections</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Vaginal infections can lead to symptoms such as foul smell, change in color, and increase in the quantity of vaginal discharge, itching, irritation, or burning sensation. These symptoms can be embarrassing as well as bothersome. Betadine Vaginal Pessaries helps in effectively managing these symptoms by killing the organisms responsible for causing an infection of the vagina that can lead to such offensive symptoms. Use Betadine Vaginal Pessaries as prescribed by the doctor to get maximum benefit. Besides, always maintain good personal hygiene to avoid any vaginal infection. Always wipe from front to back after using the toilet each time, wear cotton underpants, bathe daily and avoid the use of any sprays or deodorized products in the vaginal area. Consult your doctor if you have any doubts.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611219003.jpg', '', 150.00, NULL, '10 pessaries in 1 packet', NULL, 1, '2021-03-09 12:02:23', '2021-01-21 14:20:03'),
