(951, 1, 'B-Tex Ointment', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">B-Tex Ointment</span> is a powerful ayurvedic combination of germicide, bacteriocidal, eschorotic, antiseptic, anesthetic and anti pruritic. It is useful for eczema, ringworm, itches, cold cracks and pimples.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Boric acid(tankan amla)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Salicylic acid</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Camphor</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Tankan amla is a germicide with powerful bacteriocidal action</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Salicylic acid is an eschorotic, being hygroscopic it removes water from the tissues</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Camphor is an anti septic, anesthatic and anti pruritic agent</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It\'s an irritation free ointment</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br>Clean the affected part with lukewarm water and apply gently.<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611229295.jpg', '', 20.00, NULL, 'BOX OF 14 GM', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 12:35:06', '2021-01-21 17:11:35');
