(955, 1, 'Budamate 200 Transhaler', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Budamate 200 Transhaler is a combination of two medicines in one inhaler. It relieves the long-term symptoms of asthma and COPD, making breathing easier. It works by inhibiting the release of certain chemical messengers that cause inflammation (swelling) and relaxes the muscles in the airways.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF BUDAMATE TRANSHALER</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Asthma</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Budamate 200 Transhaler can help prevent the onset of an asthma attack if it is taken before exercise or exposure to some “triggers”. These may include house dust, pollen, pets and cigarette smoke. This medicine will allow you to exercise more freely without worrying about getting symptoms such as wheezing, coughing and shortness of breath. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease