(1005, 1, 'Calcigard Retard 20 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Calcigard Retard Tablet is a medicine used to treat high blood pressure (hypertension) and to prevent angina (heart-related chest pain). It belongs to a class of medicines known as calcium channel blockers. It lowers blood pressure and reduces the workload of the heart. This helps prevent heart attacks and strokes. Calcigard Retard Tablet may be prescribed alone or along with other medicines. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF CALCIGARD TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Treatment of Hypertension (high blood pressure)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Calcigard Retard Tablet is a calcium channel blocker. It works by relaxing the blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This lowers your blood pressure and reduces your risk of having a stroke, a heart attack, or kidney problems in the future. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of Angina (heart-related chest pain)</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Calcigard Retard Tablet belongs to a class of medicines known as a calcium channel blockers. It works by relaxing blood vessels so that blood can flow more easily around your body. This means that more oxygen gets to your heart and reduces the risk of getting chest pain (angina). This medicine should not be used to treat chest pain which is already happening. It is used to prevent or reduce the frequency of angina attacks. This medicine needs to be taken regularly as prescribed for it to work effectively. </div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><ul class=\"DrugOverview__list___1HjxR DrugOverview__uses___1jmC3\" style=\"padding-left: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"padding-top: 8px;\">In Prevention of Heart attack</li><li style=\"padding-top: 8px;\">In Prevention of Stroke</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/020321_09_28_13.jpg', '', 31.95, NULL, 'STRIP OF 10 TABLETS', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 10:15:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1006, 1, 'Calcimax 500 Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Calcimax 500 Tablets</span> offers high potency 500 mg elemental Calcium along with essential co-factors for utilization of bio-absorbed Calcium into the bones. It is useful in ensuring an adequate intake of calcium which is vital for men and women of all ages. It is especially important for growing children, pregnancy and breast-feeding period, during and after the menopause, for elderly men and women. It is used as a dietary supplement that provides extra calcium to the body. The ingredients in the formulation help in the formation and maintenance of bones. It also helps to prevent the breakage of bones.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamin D3</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Magnesium</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Zinc</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Copper</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Boron</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Selenium</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Lysine</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It provides a rich source of calcium which contributes to the maintenance of normal bones and teeth, while vitamin D contributes to normal absorption and utilisation of calcium</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It helps in the formation and maintenance of bones</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Calcium is required to prevent breakage of bones</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamin D3 helps to treat low calcium levels and high phosphate levels</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It helps the body to absorb more calcium from food and other dietary supplements</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It is indicated in the treatment of osteopenia, osteoporosis, arthritis, and fractures</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br>Use as directed by the physician.<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611231468.gif', '', 327.00, NULL, 'STRIP OF 30 TABLETS', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 10:15:09', '2021-01-21 17:47:48'),
(1007, 1, 'Calcimax D Suspension', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Calcimax D Suspension</span> contains Calcium, Magnesium, Zinc, and Vitamin D3 as an active ingredient. This combination plays an important role in the bone remodelling cycle, weak bones, and decreased activity of parathyroid gland. <br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key benefits/uses of Calcimax D Suspension:</span><br>- Increasing absorption of Calcium and Phosphorus required for strong bones<br>- Completing the need for Magnesium in the body<br>- Regulates the Calcium and Phosphate homeostasis and bone mineralization<br>- Helps in increasing the immune responses and growth and development of the body<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Direction for use/Dosage:</span><br>As directed by the physician <br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/020321_09_20_19.jpg', '', 130.00, NULL, '1 BOTTLE OF 200 ML', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 10:14:45', '2021-01-21 17:49:16'),
(1008, 1, 'Calcimax Forte Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information about Calcimax Forte+ Tablet</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Calcimax Forte Tablets</span>&nbsp;can be used as a dietary supplement that provides extra calcium to the body. It may also be used by certain patients to make sure they are getting enough calcium. Calcium plays an important role in the body. It is necessary for the normal functioning of nerves, cells, muscles, and bones. If there is not enough calcium in the blood, then the body will take calcium from bones, thereby weakening the bones. Calcimax forte is used to treat low calcium levels and high phosphate levels. It helps the body to absorb more calcium from food and other dietary supplements.&nbsp;<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Calcium carbonate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamin D3</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Magnesium</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Zinc</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It is used to treat low calcium levels and high phosphate levels</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It helps the body to absorb more calcium from food and other dietary supplements</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It is indicated in the condition of PIH &amp; pre-eclampsia in pregnancy, postpartum bone loss and lactation, diabetes, Thyroid disorders, amenorrhea, osteoporosis and osteopenia</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It provides relief in calcium and vitamin D3 deficient conditions</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It can be used as a dietary supplement that provides extra calcium to the body</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions or Use</span><br>Use as directed by the physician.<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611231619.jpg', '', 205.00, NULL, 'STRIP OF 30 TABLETS', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 10:14:17', '2021-01-21 17:50:19'),
(1009, 1, 'Calcimax ISO Capsule', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Calcimax ISO Capsule is a combination medicine that is used in the treatment of postmenopausal osteoporosis. It regulates calcium absorption in the body and strengthens the bones. It helps in the growth and development of muscles, nervous system, and heart.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF CALCIMAX CAPSULE</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Post menopausal osteoporosis</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611304658.jpg', '', 312.00, NULL, 'STRIP OF 15 CAPSULES', NULL, 1, '2021-03-03 10:13:40', '2021-01-22 14:07:38'),
