(1162, 16, 'Cavifast Paste', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Cavifast Toothpaste contains Potassium nitrate and Sodium monofluorophosphate in a pleasantly flavoured base. Cavifast Toothpaste protects against sensitivity, fights cavities and plaque, fights gum problems and strengthens tooth enamel.  It is used in sensitivity due to attrition and abrasion (wear and tear of teeth), natural gum recession or post scaling recession and abrasion on the neck of the tooth. All the ingredients in Cavifast toothpaste block the nerve that carries the message of pain due to sensitivity to the brain. This protects the tooth and keeps away the feeling of pain when eating and drinking. This toothpaste should be used on a regular basis for at least one month to get the maximum benefit. You may also massage some of the paste onto the sensitive areas after brushing.<br> <br>Directions of use: Brush properly twice daily for two minutes with this toothpaste and don\'t rinse after brushing for at least 30 minutes as it needs some time to act on teeth. By spitting thoroughly instead of rinsing your mouth with water after brushing, the thin coating of toothpaste remains on your teeth and provides the relief it is designed to give you.<br> <br>Use under medical supervision.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_06_17_51.jpg', '', 85.00, NULL, '1 tube of 100 gm paste', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 06:52:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1164, 16, 'Cavisan dental cream', 'TOOTH PASTE', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_06_38_58.jpg', '', 80.00, NULL, '1 tube of 100 gm paste', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 06:58:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1165, 1, 'Cavit-PM Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Cavit PM Tablet is a calcium supplement which contains Calcium carbonate, Magnesium oxide, Isoflavone, and Vitamin D3. Due to a decrease in estrogen production after menopause, women\'s bodies are less able to retain calcium from dietary sources. Calcium supplementation has been used to prevent this calcium depletion, maintain bone mass, and prevent and treat osteoporosis<br><br>Benefits of key ingredients:</div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br>Calcium is a mineral that is required for the formation of bones and maintaining them. Calcium is required to prevent breakage of bones. Calcium is used to prevent or treat low blood calcium levels in people who do not get enough calcium from their diets.<br>Vitamin D3 help maintain calcium levels and help the body use calcium and phosphate to maintain healthy bones. Vitamin D is used for treating conditions in which calcium metabolism is disturbed. It is also used in disorders associated with Vitamin D deficiency and in calcium malabsorption.<br>Isoflavones prevent bone loss and promote bone health and strength.<br>Magnesium are necessary for bone mineralization and bone matrix formation.<br><br>Cavit PM Tablet is also used in elderly women to keep bones healthy and strong and is use as a dietary supplements, for postmenopausal women<br><br>Use under medical Supervision</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_39_01.jpg', '', 180.00, NULL, '15 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:03:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1166, 1, 'New Cavit Syrup Mango', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__product-description___1PfGf\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify;\">Cavit syrup contains Calcium, Vitamin D3(cholecalciferol) which is used to it ensures the adequate supply of calcium to bones.<br>&nbsp;<br>Calcium ensures the adequate supply of calcium to bones. It may be used to treat conditions caused by low calcium levels such as breaking of bones.<br>Vitamin D3(cholecalciferol) that is used in the absorption of calcium in the blood. Vitamin D3 helps in processing of essential minerals in the body like Calcium and Phosphorus. Lack of Vitamin D3 results in bone weakening, bone pain, and skin diseases.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Cavit is a nutritional supplement which can be taken by people who have low levels of calcium in their blood.Cavit is used in elderly people to keep bones healthy and strong, and is even effective in Chronic arthritis and Osteoporosis.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Use under medical supervision.&nbsp;</div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_44_06.jpg', '', 109.90, NULL, '150 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:06:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
