(1427, 16, 'Clohex ADS Mouthwash', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Clohex ADS Liquid</span> is a chemical antiseptic which is prescribed for removing and reducing the bacteria in the mouth. It helps in cleansing the wounded areas on the skin.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Chlorhexidine gluconate 0.20 %W/V</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sodium fluoride 0.05 %W/V</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Zinc chloride 0.09 %W/V</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps in treating a gum disease that causes inflamed gums</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Reduces the irritation, redness and the swelling around the gums</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It helps to cleanse or deodorize the teeth and mouth</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use</span><br>Use as directed by the physician.<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_56_17.jpg', '', 179.75, NULL, '1 Bottle of 200 ml Mouth Wash', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:22:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1428, 16, 'CLOHEX-MOUTHWASH 1*150ML', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Clohex Mouth Wash is a used in the treatment of inflammation of gums. It kills the harmful microorganisms in the oral cavity that cause swollen gums, and tartar, bad odor from mouth. This way it cleans the affected area and speeds up healing.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF CLOHEX MOUTH WASH</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Inflammation of gums</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Whenever there is an overgrowth of microorganisms in our mouth, that are otherwise normally present, it can lead to unpleasant symptoms suggestive of mouth infection. These symptoms include bad breath, swollen gums, unpleasant taste changes, sensitivity of teeth to hot or cold food/liquid etc. Clohex Mouth Wash kills and prevents growth of these bacteria, thereby relieving these symptoms. This helps in maintaining good oral hygiene.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_40_21.jpg', '', 112.00, NULL, '150 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:21:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
