(1754, 15, 'D Acne Foaming Face Wash', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">D Acne Foaming Face Wash contains Aloe Vera Extract, Glycolic acid and Salicylic Acid as key ingredients and Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycol Disterate, Glycerin, PEG-8 Carbomer, PEF-12 Dimethicone, Trometamol, Citric Acid as other ingredients.<br>- A daily face wash for acne free face<br>- Provides clear look to the face<br><br>Key benefits/uses of D Acne Foaming Face Wash:<br>- Aloe Vera Extract is antibacterial, anti-inflammatory, pain inhibitor astringent, scar reducing property and stimulates cell growth<br>- Salicylic Acid is used as an exfoliant, helps to shed dead skin cells from its follicles and thus keeps the pores clean of it cellular debris<br>- Glycolic Acid penetrates the skin and is effective in the treatment of fine lines, acne, blackheads etc.<br>- Keeps skin free from acne-prone infections<br>- Controls sebum secretion<br>- Suitable for all skin types especially acne prone skin<br><br>Directions of use/ Dosage:<br>- Wet the face<br>- Massage gently on face to form god lather<br>- Rinse thoroughly with water and pat dry<br>- Use twice a day for better results<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_35_37.jpg', '', 449.00, NULL, '1 Pump bottle of 60 ml Face Wash', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:37:46', '2021-01-27 16:51:37'),
(1755, 15, 'D Acne Gel', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">D Acne Gel is an antibiotic that fights bacteria. It is used to treat acne, which appears as spots or pimples on your face, chest or back. This medicine works by attacking the bacteria that cause these pimples.<br><br>D Acne Gel is only meant for external use and should be used as advised by your doctor.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF D ACNE GEL</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Acne</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">D Acne Gel is an antibiotic that works by stopping the growth of bacteria causing acne on your skin.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_14_43.jpg', '', 129.00, NULL, '10 gm in 1 tube', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:43:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1756, 15, 'D Acne Soap', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">D Acne Soap contains Salicylic acid and Clindamycin as main active ingredients.<br>- Nourishes and keeps the skin moisturized treat acne effectively<br>- Reduces keratinization and inhibits acne-causing bacteria<br><br>Key benefits/uses of D Acne Soap:<br>- Salicylic acid is a peeling agent that leads to the shedding of the outer layer of skin to treat Acne, Seborrheic Dermatitis, and other skin problems<br>- Clindamycin is an antibiotic and treats the number of bacterial infections<br><br>Direction of Use/ Dosage:<br>- Replace other ordinary soaps to wash face<br>- For better results use regularly<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_39_45.jpg', '', 225.00, NULL, '1 packet of 75 gm soap', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:45:39', '2021-01-27 16:58:20'),
(1757, 15, 'D Acne Soft Face Wash', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">D Acne Soft Face Wash</span> is used to treat mild to moderate acne. It may be used in combination with other acne treatments. <br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:<br></span><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sodium Lauryl Ether Sulphate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Cocoamidopropyl Betaine</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Glycerine</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sorbitol 70 and Niacinamide</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:<br></span><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Clears dirt and impurities from the skin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Provides deep cleansing action on pores</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Reduces the germs and bacteria which cause acne</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Prevents excessive dryness of the skin</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Direction For Use: </span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Moisten face and neck and take an adequate amount</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Massage gently till the lather forms</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Clean with water and dry</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>For better result, use daily</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_30_47.jpg', '', 310.00, NULL, '1 Tube of 100 gm Face Wash', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:47:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(1758, 15, 'Daffy Bathing Bar', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Daffy bathing Soap</span>&nbsp;is a soap-free bathing bar with pH same as healthy skin pH 5.5. Daffy is enriched with the goodness of shea and aloe butter.<br>&nbsp;<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Shea Butter</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Aloe vera</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Shea butter is considered to be an excellent moisturizer which maintains and preserves the acid content</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Shea butter is well tolerated by the skin, it doesn’t trigger any allergic reactions</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It acts as an inflammatory agent in various inflammatory skin disorders</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Aloe vera and shea butter acts as an anti-oxidant which prevents damage to the skin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Daffy is very mild on the baby’s delicate skin thus providing nourishment and complete protection for healthy skin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Daffy maintains moistures in the outermost layer (epidermis) of the skin and keeps the baby`s skin smooth and supple</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br>Gently apply to the baby\'s skin and rinse off with water. Discontinue use if skin irritation occurs.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611747095.jpg', '', 157.50, NULL, '1 Packet of 75 gm Soap', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:49:39', '2021-01-27 17:01:35'),
