(1873, 15, 'Dermadew Acne Soap', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Dermadew Acne Soap contains gentle cleanser combined with anti-acne actives of both natural and the synthetic origin and fortified with specific emollients, moisturizers, and skin nourishers. Dermadew Acne Soap gives smooth, soft, supple and fresh feeling to the skin. For better results use Dermadew Acne Soap as adjuvant along with anti-acne medications. <br> <br>It contains Sodium palmate, sodium palm kernelate, aqua, perfume, triclosan,ethyl lactate, zinc PCA, salicylic acid, manuka concentrate, willow extract, tea tree oil, olive extract, aloe barbadensis extract, glycerin, sodium chloride, titanium dioxide, disodium EDTA, disodium etidronate, butylated hydroxytoluene.<br> <br>Dermadew Acne soap has Mild and beautiful fragrance. It Forms rich foam and effectively cleanses away dirt and oil without leaving out the skin dry.<br>It prevents the occurrence of new pimples and dries out existing pimples fast. It also Helps in fading the marks left by pimples. Dermadew acne soap mattifies the skin and keeps it oil free for 2-3 hours. This soap is very gentle on even the driest areas of the skin. It gives a nice glow to the face and brightens it up.<br> <br>Use under medical supervision</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_07_26_54.jpg', '', 175.00, NULL, '1 Packet of 75 gm Soap', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:54:26', '2021-01-28 17:07:54');
