(1874, 15, 'Dermadew Aloe Cream', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Dermadew Aloe Cream contains Aloe vera gel, light liquid paraffin, and white soft paraffin. Dermadew is best used emollient and potent moisturiser acts by hydrating the skin, makes skin soft, silky &amp; supple. It protects the skin from drying, chipping and getting scaley.<br>Light liquid paraffin and white soft paraffin works by providing a layer of oil on the surface of the skin to prevent water evaporating from the skin surface.<br>Aloe vera is reputed for its skin soothing and moisturizing properties.<br>&nbsp;<br>Dermadew Aloe Cream helpful for dry skin conditions, particularly eczema and dermatitis, which get worse when the skin is allowed to dry out.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Used regularly they help restore the skin\'s smoothness, softness and flexibility by helping the skin retain moisture.<br>&nbsp;<br>Use under medical supervision.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611833955.jpg', '', 180.00, NULL, '1 Tube of 50 gm Cream', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:56:27', '2021-01-28 17:09:15'),
(1875, 15, 'Dermadew Aloe Lotion', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Dermadew is a dermatological preparation indicated for various disorders of the skin, especially dry skin.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Dermadew contains Aloe Vera gel 10% w/w and glycerin 10% w/w in a moisturizing lotion base of dimethicone and hydrogenated polydecene.<br>Role of key ingredients:<br>Aloe Vera is an extract from the leaves of the plant Aloe Vera. It contains 90% water, inorganic compounds, protein and acemannan. Acemannan transports nutrients to the cells and nourishes them. Glycerin is a sugar alcohol; it improves smoothness by binding water to the skin and prevents moisture loss.<br>Dermadew aloe moisturizes and protects the skin and is useful for various dry skin conditions.<br>&nbsp;<br>Directions of use:&nbsp;<br>Apply in adequate amounts two or three time a day by gentle massage.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Use under medical supervision</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611834038.jpg', '', 180.00, NULL, '1 Bottle of 50 ml Lotion', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:58:17', '2021-01-28 17:10:38'),
(1876, 3, 'Dermadew Baby Lotion', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Dermadew Baby Lotion</span>&nbsp;contains almond oil and turmeric oil fortified with specific emollients, moisturizers, and skin nourishers. Dermadew baby lotion is recommended for your baby\'s delicate skin. It makes the skin soft, smooth, supple and improves skin tone.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Aloe vera</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamin E</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Shea butter</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Turmeric oil</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Almond oil</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Gentle, hypoallergenic and pH neutral formula for gentle skin of the baby</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Rich in moisturizers that gently moisturizes skin for up to 24 Hours</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Soothes your baby\'s dry skin from the first use</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br>Apply Dermadew Baby Lotion all over the baby\'s body after bath.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611834210.jpg', '', 115.00, NULL, '1 Bottle of 80 ml Lotion', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 07:59:34', '2021-01-28 17:13:30'),
(1877, 3, 'Dermadew Baby Soap', 'BABY SOAP', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611834288.jpg', '', 155.00, NULL, '1 Box of 75 gm Soap', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 08:00:37', '2021-01-28 17:14:48'),
(1878, 15, 'Dermadew Face Wash', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Dermadew face wash</span> is a sulphate free, gentle natural cleanser that helps in making the skin smooth, soft, supple and refreshed. The face wash is suitable for all skin types and helps in complete nourishment of the skin. This is dermatologically tested and safe for skin.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Aloe vera pea extract in a sulphate free natural moisturizing base</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps in removing excess sebum</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps in nourishement of the skin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps in keeping the skin moisturized and soft</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Apply Dermadew face wash on wet face and neck, work into creamy lather by massaging in upward circular motion, rinse off and dry</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611834371.jpg', '', 209.00, NULL, '1 Tube of 100 ml Face Wash', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 08:03:37', '2021-01-28 17:16:11'),
(1879, 15, 'Dermadew Soap', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Dermadew Soap contains vegetable oils fortified with specific emollients, moisturisers and skin nourishers. It contains Palm and Coconut Oil soap noodles, Kokum Butter, Glycerin, Aloe Vera Extract and Olive Extract.<br>Benefits of active Ingredients:<br>&nbsp;<br>Palm oil: Contains a high concentration of Vitamin E &amp; helps restores the skin natural oils.<br>Coconut Oil: Moisturize the skin &amp; remove dirt and dead cells from the skin. &nbsp;<br>Kokum Butter: Promotes skin elasticity, restoration of damaged skin and prevent skin dryness.<br>Glycerin: Help to keep the skin silky smooth and well hydrated.<br>Aloe Vera Extract: Naturally antibacterial, promotes skin health and hydration<br>&nbsp;<br>Dermadew soap is recommended for all age groups. It makes the skin soft, supple, well hydrated and improves skin tone.<br>&nbsp;<br>Use under medical supervision</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611834636.jpg', '', 149.00, NULL, '1 Packet of 75 gm Soap', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 08:03:03', '2021-01-28 17:20:36'),
