(1907, 6, 'Dexolac 2 Follow-Up Formula Refill Pack', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\"><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33);\"></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33);\">Dexolac 2 is a healthy spray dried follow up formula for infants. This is high quality milk substitute for infants who are 6 to 12 months old. It is formulated especially for the growth of babies. It provides a great level of energy to support development. Enriched with Choline, Omega 3 and 6 fatty acids, Iodine and Iron, it is useful for baby\'s brain development. It contains Vitamin D, Calcium and Magnesium to build stronger bones of babies. By providing great amount of Iron, this nutrition prevents the iron deficiency anemia.<br> <br>Key Benefits:<br>Best milk substitute for infant from 6 to 12 months old<br>Rich in energy to support growth of babies<br>Helps to build stronger bones<br>Develops sharp brain<br>Provides great amount of iron to prevent iron deficiency anemia<br>Improves the development of useful gut bacteria in infants<br>Contains vitals nutrients for development<br> <br> <br> <br>Use under Medical supervision.</div></h2></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1611914158.jpg', '', 304.00, NULL, '1 packet of 500 gm', NULL, 1, '2021-03-08 13:35:26', '2021-01-29 15:25:58'),
