(2347, 7, 'Enfagrow A+ Stage 4 Nutritional Milk Powder (3-6 Years) Chocolate', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\"><br></h2><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Enfagrow A+ Stage 4 Nutritional Milk Powder</span>&nbsp;is a unique blend of essential nutrients including DHA, prebiotics and various micronutrients. These nutrients help to support a child\'s immune health. The formula helps meet nutrient RDA levels and alleviates deficiency of important nutrients in the body. Source of DHA plus, Iron, Zinc, Vitamin B6 and B12, Folate etc. Supports all-round development including brain development, immunity and overall physical growth and health.&nbsp; Provides these vital nutrients such as Vitamin B12, Choline, Zinc, Iron and Iodine for the mental and physical development of the child.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;<br></span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Milk Solids (57%) (whole milk powder, skimmed milk powder)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Glucose syrup solids</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sucrose</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Cocoa powder (3%)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Minerals</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Dietary fibers (fructo-oligosacchharides, inulin)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA) from Crypthecodinium cohnii</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamins</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Stabilizer (carrageenan)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Contains added flavour</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key benefits:<br></span><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Respiratory health:&nbsp;</span>DHA, zinc, Vitamin A and C support and maintaining respiratory health</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Highest DHA and reduced sugar:&nbsp;</span>Enfagrow A+ now offers the highest DHA among all kids\' nutrition products and reduced sugar</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Gut health:</span>&nbsp;Vitamin A, Zinc and Prebiotics maintains gut health</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Better Immunity:&nbsp;</span>Enfagrow A+ contains Vitamins A, B, C, E, Iron, Zinc, and Pre-Biotics which build 3 types of immunity: respiratory health, digestive health, and resistance to infection</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Physical growth:</span>&nbsp;Enfagrow A+ has Calcium, Vitamin D, Phosphorus, and Magnesium to promote growth</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Brain development:&nbsp;</span>Supports holistic development of the brain including intellectual, motor, emotional and communication skill</li></ul><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Direction for use/Dosage:</span></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Method for preparation</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Wash all feeding utensils and sterilize thoroughly before preparation</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>For a single serving, add 3 level scoops of the powder to a previously boiled warm water (120ml)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Stir properly and shake well</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>&nbsp;Use the scoop of the can to measure the powder. 3 servings per day are recommended. It can be mixed with water or milk, to make a healthy and tasty drink for the toddler<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;</span></li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/090321_06_35_49.webp', '', 625.00, NULL, '1 tin of 400 gm powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-09 06:49:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(2348, 6, 'Enfamil A+ Stage 1 Infant Formula', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Enfamil A+ Stage 1 Infant Formula Powder </span>is a complete blend of DHA, essential Vitamins and Minerals required for the complete growth and maintenance of newly born baby.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"> </span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key benefits/uses of Enfamil A+ Stage 1 Infant Formula:</span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">-</span> DHA is an important building block of the baby\'s developing brain.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">- </span>The ingredients provide complete support for baby\'s development.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">-</span> The formulation is easy to digest by the baby.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"> </span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Direction for use/Dosage:</span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">(Method for preparation)</span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Step 1) </span>Wash hand thoroughly using soap and water before preparing the formula for infant feeding.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Step 2) </span>Sterilize clean bottles, nipples, caps and utensils by boiling in water for 5 minutes<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Step 3) </span>For five minutes boil fresh water, cool to room temperature and pour the desired amount of cooled boiled water into the bottle and add the content.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Step 4)</span> Put a cap on the bottle and shake well.<br> <br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Storage instructions:</span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">- </span>Store in a cool and dry place.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">- </span>After opening the pack keep it tightly covered, keep in a dry area and use the content within one month.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">- </span>Do not freeze the powder and avoid excessive heat.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/090321_06_56_52.jpg', '', 715.00, NULL, '1 tin of 400 gm powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-09 06:56:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(2349, 6, 'Enfamil A+ Stage 2 Follow Up Formula', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Enfamil A+ Stage 2 Follow Up Formula Powder</span> is a complete blend of DHA, essential Vitamins and Minerals required for the complete growth and maintenance of newly born baby.<br>The formula is intended for babies from 6 months up to 12 months.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"> </span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key benefits/uses of Enfamil A+ Stage 2 Follow Up Formula Powder:</span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">- </span>DHA is an important building block of the baby\'s developing brain.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">- </span>The ingredients present in the formulation support complete development of the baby.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">- </span>The formulation is easy to digest by the baby.<br> <br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Direction for use/Dosage:</span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">(Method for preparation)</span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Step 1) </span>Wash hand thoroughly using soap and water before preparing the formula for infant feeding.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Step 2) </span>Sterilize clean bottles, nipples, caps and utensils by boiling in water for 5 minutes<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Step 3)</span> For five minutes boil fresh water, cool to room temperature and pour the desired amount of cooled boiled water into the bottle and add the content.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Step