(2356, 7, 'Ensure Diabetes Care Vanilla delight Powder (1 kg)', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Ensure Diabetes Care Powder</span> is diabetes-specific nutrition for diabetic patients. The Ensure powder for diabetics is scientifically formulated with slow-release energy system to help manage blood glucose levels and support weight management. The Ensure Diabetes Care Powder provides steady energy and helps to keep blood glucose and weight under control.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Maltodextrin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Calcium Caseinate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Edible Vegetable Oils (High Oleic Sunflower Oil, Soy Oil)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Fructose, Cocoa Powder</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Fructooligosaccharide (FOS)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Soy Polysaccharide</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>M-Inositol</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamins</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Antioxidants (Soy Lecithin, Mixed Tocopherols) Taurine</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>L-Carnitine</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sucralose</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps manage blood sugar and supports weight management</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps build muscle mass</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It supports heart and digestive health</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Contains high-quality protein and sucralose (an artificial sweetener)</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Free from lactose trans fat and gluten</li></ul> <br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br>To prepare a glass of approximately 237 ml, combine 6 scoops (52 g) of powder with 200 ml of water. As a partial meal replacement- 1 serving of Ensure can be used before a major meal (eg. lunch/ dinner), as a breakfast replacement, evening/ bedtime snack or as directed by physician/ dietician.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1612093827.jpg', '', 1490.00, NULL, '1 box of 1 kg powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-09 07:02:29', '2021-01-31 17:20:27'),
