(3136, 16, 'Glizer Toothpaste', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Glizer toothpaste is a fixed dose combination of disodium monofluorophosphate, zinc sulphate and aluminium is used as mouth preparations for removal of plaque . Glizer toothpaste brightens the teeth with its continuous use. It is also used for cleaning of denture and teeth.<br>It’s a foaming fluoridated toothpaste that contains natural ingredients like neem, bromelain, Meswak. It is an effective natural whitener toothpaste that also helps to hold the gum to teeth.</div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Directions for use:<br>Brush with this paste twice a day for atleast two minutes and donot swallow.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_12_45_51.jpg', '', 111.00, NULL, '1 Tube of 100 gm Toothpaste', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 12:51:45', '2021-02-18 17:20:30'),
