(3443, 16, 'Himalaya Hiora-GA Gum Astringent Gel', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HiOra GA gel is a herbal gum astringent gel.It has astringent (that contracts the soft tissue and reduces bleeding) and antiseptic properties. It is a haemostatic (stops bleeding) that prevents gum bleeding and helps in strengthening gums. The gel reduces gum inflammation, heals wounds, refreshes breath and kills bacteria in the oral cavity. Its natural ingredients act as analgesics to reduce pain inside the mouth. It contains Triphala that inhibits bacterial growth and Indian Kino Tree (Asana) that has astringent and anti-inflammatory properties, which are helpful in reducing pain and stopping gum bleeding.<br><br>Directions for use:&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Apply the gum paint with your finger or cotton applicator on the gums and massage, after brushing and do not rinse or eat for at least 10 minutes. This helps the gum paint to get absorbed in the gums and helps in healing of the gums and they become more firm.<br>&nbsp;<br>Use under medical supervision.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1614423280.jpg', '', 55.00, NULL, '1 Bottle of 15 ml Gum Paint', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 13:11:28', '2021-02-27 16:24:40'),
(3444, 16, 'Himalaya Hiora-K Toothpaste', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Himalaya Hiora-K Toothpaste</span> is useful for sensitive teeth and gums. Formulated with the natural ingredients, it forms a protective covering around enamel of teeth and provides relief from pain and the tingling sensation caused due to sensitive teeth.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Spinach</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Potassium Nitrate</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Clove</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Provides relief from pain and tingling sensation by desensitizing dental nerves</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps in formation of a protective layer on tooth enamel</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps in strengthening of gums</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps in preventing enamel erosion</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Protects from oral bacteria</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use</span><br>Brush twice daily until symptoms subside or as directed by the dentist</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/110321_13_47_13.jpg', '', 84.00, NULL, '1 Tube of 100 gm Toothpaste', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 13:14:12', '2021-02-27 16:26:59'),
(3445, 16, 'Himalaya Hiora-K Mouth Wash', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HiOra-K Mouthwash contains natural potassium that reduces tooth sensitivity and restores the mineral composition of teeth, strengthening them as a result. HiOra-K Mouthwash also eliminates bad breath, refreshes the mouth and maintains oral hygiene.<br>&nbsp;<br>Key ingredients:<br>Suryakshara:- Naturally derived Potassium nitrate (Suryakshara) inhibits pain in hypersensitive teeth through its desensitizing effect on dentinal nerves.<br>Lavanga:- Clove (Lavanga) contains an anesthetic chemical compound, which numbs nerves and stops pain. The essential oil of clove is also an antiseptic, which helps eliminate oral bacteria.<br>&nbsp;<br>Directions for use:<br>Take 15 ml of mouthwash. Rinse mouth thoroughly for 30 seconds and expel. Use twice daily.<br>&nbsp;<br>Use under medical supervision.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1614423888.jpg', '', 75.00, NULL, '1 Bottle of 150 ml Mouth Wash', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 13:15:13', '2021-02-27 16:34:48'),
(3447, 16, 'Himalaya Hiora Mouth Wash', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">The Himalaya HiOra Mouth Wash</span>&nbsp;kills germs, tones gums &amp; refreshes mouth. Useful in plaque, gingivitis, and halitosis.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Bibhitaki</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Betel</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Meswak</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Acts as antimicrobial and antiseptic</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Fights against oral bacteria and fungi</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Reduces gum and tooth disease as well as the build-up of plaque</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps strengthen and tone gums</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Reduces bad breath, refreshes mouth and maintains oral hygiene</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Has stimulating properties are beneficial for toothaches</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Acts as teeth-cleaning agents</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Prevents tooth decay and eliminates toothache and bad breath</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Take 15 ml of mouthwash</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Rinse mouth thoroughly for 30 seconds and expel</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Use twice daily</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1614424426.jpg', '', 75.00, NULL, '1 Bottle of 150 ml Mouth Wash', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 13:17:16', '2021-02-27 16:43:46'),
(3448, 16, 'Himalaya Hiora SG Gel', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Himalaya Hiora-SG gel contains jasmine (jati), licorice (yashtimadhu), spreading hogweed (punarnava) and triphala as its ingredient.<br> <br>Key benefits of Himalaya Hiora-SG gel:</div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">The antibacterial, anti-inflammatory, anti-allergic, wound-healing and analgesic properties of the gel help to heal mouth ulcers quickly.<br>The gel also modulates the body’s immune response and prevents the recurrence of mouth ulcers.<br>Relieves teething pain. It also relieves pain and irritation caused by dentures.<br> <br>Direction for use:<br>Take a small amount of the gel on the tip of a clean finger and apply gently over the affected areas. Repeat application three to five times per day or as directed by the dentist or doctor.<br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/1614424491.jpg', '', 55.00, NULL, '1 Tube of 10 gm Gel', NULL, 1, '2021-03-11 13:19:00', '2021-02-27 16:44:51'),
