(3889, 6, 'Lactodex 3 Powder', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Lactodex 3 Powder contains Protein, Milk Fats, Linoleic Acid, a-Linolenic Acid, Polyunsaturated Fatty Acids, Monounsaturated Fatty Acids, Saturated Fatty Acids, Cholesterol, Trans Fatty Acids, Carbohydrate, Sugar (Sucrose), Minerals (Ash), Moisture, Vitamin C, Choline, Vitamin E, Pantothenic Acid, Nicotinamide, Vitamin A, Vitamin B2, Vitamin B6, Vitamin B1, Vitamin B12, Folic Acid, Biotin, Vitamin K, Vitamin D, Vitamin B1, Calcium, Potassium, Phosphorus, Chloride, Sodium and Magnesium, Iron, Zinc, Copper, Iodine, Manganese, and Selenium as major ingredients.<br>This is a Follow-Up formula for infants ageing between 10 -24 months of age to support the normal growth and development of the infant.<br><br>Key benefits/uses of Lactodex 3 Powder:<br>- Used to treat the deficiency of various vital nutrients including essential vitamins &amp; minerals in the body which play a key role in the growth and development of the infant.<br>- Used for the treatment of weight loss, malnutrition and other problems.<br><br>Directions for use/Dosage: Use the formulation as directed on the pack or as directed by the healthcare professional.<br><br>Indication:<br>Nutritional deficiency in infants</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/060321_12_49_42.jpg', '', 465.00, NULL, '1 tin of 450 gm powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-06 12:42:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(3890, 6, 'Nestle Lactogen Stage 1 Powder Refill', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Nestle Lactogen Stage 1 Powder is a spray dried powdered form of milk. Lactogen 1 is a spray dried infant formula for infants upto six months when they are not breastfed. The powder contains Maltodexrin, Milk solids, Demineralised whey, Soyabeal oil, Corn oil, Minerals, Soya lecithin, Vitamins, Taurine and L-Carnitine.<br>It also contains essential nutrients that help in the growth of the infants and also help in the development of the brain. &nbsp;The powder additionally also contains essential fatty acids such as alanine and choline which serve as the building blocks of the brain. Iron regulates the process of blood formation whereas Iodine avoids the inflammation of the thyroid.<br>All put together, the powder contains 14 vitamins and 12 minerals that together contribute towards the effective growth and development of the infants.<br><br>Benefits of Nestle Lactogen Stage 1 Powder:<br>For growth of the baby<br>For brain development of the baby<br>For healthy vision for energy needs<br><br>Important Notice:<br>Mother\'s milk is best for your baby<br><br>Use under medical supervision</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/060321_12_44_48.jpg', '', 330.00, NULL, '1 box of 400 gm powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-06 12:48:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(3891, 6, 'Nestle Lactogen Stage 1 Powder Tin', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Nestle Lactogen Stage 1 Powder is a spray dried powdered form of milk. Lactogen 1 is a spray dried infant formula for infants upto six months when they are not breastfed. The powder contains Maltodexrin, Milk solids, Demineralised whey, Soyabeal oil, Corn oil, Minerals, Soya lecithin, Vitamins, Taurine and L-Carnitine.<br>It also contains essential nutrients that help in the growth of the infants and also help in the development of the brain.  The powder additionally also contains essential fatty acids such as alanine and choline which serve as the building blocks of the brain. Iron regulates the process of blood formation whereas Iodine avoids the inflammation of the thyroid.<br>All put together, the powder contains 14 vitamins and 12 minerals that together contribute towards the effective growth and development of the infants.<br><br>Benefits of Nestle Lactogen Stage 1 Powder:<br>For growth of the baby<br>For brain development of the baby<br>For healthy vision for energy needs<br><br>Important Notice:<br>Mother\'s milk is best for your baby<br><br>Use under medical supervision</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/060321_12_11_51.jpg', '', 325.00, NULL, '1 tin of 450 gm powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-06 12:52:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(3893, 6, 'Nestle Lactogen Stage 2 Powder Refill', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Nestle Lactogen 2 is a spray dried follow up formula designed for healthy infants as the liquid part of the diet during and after weaning. It is not to be used as a breast milk substitute during the first six months of life.<br><br>Nestle Lactogen 2 contains Maltodextrin which is easy to digest and nutrients that support growth brain development. Infant almost triple their weight by 1st year of life. An infant needs important nutrients like protein, minerals and vitamins that are essential for growth development.Nestle Lactogen 2 contains 12 minerals and 14 vitamins. Nestle Lactogen 2 contains Maltodextrin which is an easy to digest carbohydrate.<br>Alpha Lipoic Aicd, ALA (omega 3 fatty acid (FA) and LA (omega 6 FA) are the precursors of DHA and ARA. ALA, an essential Omega 3 fatty acid contributes to brain development. Iron loadline also help in brain development.Nestle Lactogen 2 contains essential fatty acid ALA (Omega 3 FA), LA (Omega 6 FA) along with Choline, loadline iron and vitamin A. Choline contributes to the structural building block of the brain. Vitamin A contributes to healthy vision.<br><br>Benefits of Nestle Lactogen 2<br>Growth of the baby<br>Development of brain<br>Provides essential vitamins and omega fatty acids<br><br>Breast milk is best for your baby<br><br>Use under medical supervision.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/070321_14_56_49.jpg'