(4991, 6, 'Nestle Nan Excella Pro 1 Powder', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Nestle Nan Excella Pro 1 Infant formula</span> is a mixture of DHA and ARA for infants who are not breastfed from birth. It is made using spray dried formula. DHA and ARA are essential in promoting baby’s normal brain growth. It contains many important nutrients, such as iron iodine, choline, and whey protein. Whey protein is a component of protein found in milk, making it easier to digest.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients</span>:<br>• Calcium<br>• Phosphorous<br>• Chloride<br>• Magnesium<br>• Copper<br>• Zinc<br>• Iron<br>• Iodine<br>• Sodium<br>• Potassium<br>• Vitamin A<br>• Vitamin C<br>• Vitamin D<br>• Vitamin E<br>• Vitamin K<br>• Thiamine<br>• Riboflavin<br>• Niacin<br>• Pantothenic Acid<br>• Folic Acid<br>• Vitamin B6<br>• Vitamin B12<br>• Choline<br>• Biotin<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Uses:</span><br>• With DHA as its primary component, it helps support baby’s normal brain growth.<br>• It is used for infants who are not breastfed from birth.<br>• It contains Whey protein derived from milk protein to ensure that the baby gets all the right amount of this important nutrient.<br>• Contains many important vitamins and minerals essential for baby’s healthy development<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions for Use:</span><br>• With clean hands, sterilize the feeding bowl and spoon<br>• Pour lukewarm water as is advised in the feeding table<br>• Consult feeding table and add the exact amount of the leveled scoops for the age of the baby<br>• Use Only the scoop provided<br>• Mix well to dissolve in water<br>• Feed the baby with bowl and spoon and discard the leftover<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Safety Information:</span><br>Consult the feeding table thoroughly before using Nestle Nan Excella Pro 1</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/070321_15_57_11.jpg', '', 730.00, NULL, '1 Box of 400 gm Powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-07 15:11:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4992, 6, 'Nestle Nan Excellapro 2 Follow-Up Formula Powder', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Nestle Nan Excellapro 2 Follow-Up Formula Powder</span>&nbsp;is the product of 150 years of scientific research in the field of infant nutrition. It is a completely vegetarian product spray dried formula that is made for infants older than six months and are not being breast fed any more.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Milk Solids</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Oil mix</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamin A, C, D</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Zinc</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Calcium</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It is a spray dried formula which consists of DHA ARA needed for the development of an infant</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It is designed for infants older than six months who have stopped being breast fed</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>The DHA in it helps the proper development of the infant\'s brain</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>The box that it comes in is specifically designed to ensure safety, hygiene and convenience</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Wash hands</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sterilize utensils including the feeding bowl and spoon</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Boil drinking water for five minutes and leave it till lukewarm</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Pour the exactly needed amount of lukewarm water as per the feeding table</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Consult the feeding table and add the precise number of scoops as mentioned in the table according to the baby\'s age</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Shake or mix to dissolve the powder</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/070321_15_09_16.jpeg', '', 720.00, NULL, '1 Box of 400 gm Powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-07 15:16:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
