(4994, 6, 'Nestle Nan Lo-Lac Infant Formula Powder', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Nestle Nan Lo-Lac Infant Formula Powder</span>&nbsp;is a spray dried low lactose (upto 5%) infant formula which is suitable for infants from birth to 24 months. It is composed of various nutrients required for the physical and mental growth of the infant. It various essential nutrients which support healthy growth and development of babies.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Spray dried infant formula with low lactose (not more than 5% lactose)</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It contains vitamins and essential nutrients to promote healthy growth in infants</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Reduces the risk of food allergies</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Provides essential nutrients to the baby</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Helps in the physical and mental development of the infant</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Wash your hands before preparing baby’s formula</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Wash bottle, that stopper and cup thoroughly until no milk remains; boil for five minutes. Leave covered until use</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Boil drinking water for five minutes and allow to cool</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Consult feeding table, pour exact amount of lukewarm water into the sterilised bottle</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Only use the scoop from this container and level using leveller at an opening</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Consult feeding table, and an exact number of level scoops for the age of the baby</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Close the bottle with stopper. Shake bottle until Nestle Nan Lo Lac Infant Formula powder is fully dissolved</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Use prepared feed within half an hour of preparation otherwise microbial deterioration may set in</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Close the tin tightly after each use and store it in a cool and dry place</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/070321_15_50_21.jpg', '', 245.00, NULL, '1 Box of 200 gm Powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-07 15:21:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
