(4996, 6, 'Nestlé Pre NAN', '<h2 style=\"padding: 0px 0px 4px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Information</h2><div class=\"a-section content\" style=\"margin-bottom: 22px; margin-top: 6.5px; margin-left: 25px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><h4 style=\"padding: 0px 0px 4px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Ingredients:</h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 14px;\">Milk Solids,Demineralised Whey(22.8%),Maltodextrins,Soyabean oil,Medium chain triglycrides(MCT) Oil,Antioxidant(Soya Lecithin),Acidity regulators( Citric Acid and Potassium hydroxide),Amino acids,Oil Mix(Arachidonic acid(ARA) from Morterella Alpina oil,Docosahexaenoic acid(DHA) from crypthecodinium cohnii oil),sunflower oil,Antioxidants(Mixed tocopherol concentrate and L-Ascorbyl palmitate) ,Acidity regulator(Citric Acid),Vitamins,Turine,L-Carnitine</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 0px;\"></p></div><div class=\"a-section content\" style=\"margin-bottom: 22px; margin-top: 6.5px; margin-left: 25px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><h4 style=\"padding: 0px 0px 4px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px;\">Directions:</h4><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 14px;\">Step 1: Wash your hands. Use clean utensils. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 14px;\">Step 2: Sterilize utensils including the feeding spoon and bowl. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 14px;\">Step 3: Boil drinking water for 5 minutes and leave it till lukewarm. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 14px;\">Step 4: Pour the exact amount of lukewarm water as per feeding table. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 14px;\">Step 5: Consult the feeding table and add exactly number of leveled scoops for the age of a baby. Only use the scoop provided. Shake/mix to dissolve powder. </p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 14px;\">Step 6: Feed the baby with a bowl and spoon. Discard leftover feed.</p></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/070321_15_59_31.jpg', '', 540.00, NULL, '400 gm Tin Pack', NULL, 1, '2021-03-07 15:31:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
