(6210, 7, 'Protinex Junior Powder Chocolate (250 gm)', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Protinex Junior is a specially formulated, balanced nutritional supplement that promotes all round physical and mental growth in children during the critical growing up years. <br> <br>Role of key ingredients: <br>Whey, Milk and Soy protein provides high protein content for physical growth, <br>DHA for mental development <br>34 essential vitamins and minerals including Calcium, Iron and Iodine<br>Additionally it contains FOS (Fructo-Oliga-Saccharides) a natural soluble fibre which promotes digestive health, thereby helping to build immunity.<br> <br>Directions of use:<br>Add 5 scoops (45 gm) to a glass of lukewarm milk (200 ml). <br>Stir until dissolved. <br>Add sugar to taste.<br> <br>Available in Vanilla flavour.<br> <br>Use under medical supervision.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/080321_07_19_51.jpg', '', 365.00, NULL, '1 tin of 200 gm powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-08 07:51:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6211, 7, 'Protinex Junior Powder Vanilla (400 gm)', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Protinex Junior is a specially formulated, balanced nutritional supplement that promotes all round physical and mental growth in children during the critical growing up years. <br> <br>Role of key ingredients: <br>Whey, Milk and Soy protein provides high protein content for physical growth, <br>DHA for mental development <br>34 essential vitamins and minerals including Calcium, Iron and Iodine<br>Additionally it contains FOS (Fructo-Oliga-Saccharides) a natural soluble fibre which promotes digestive health, thereby helping to build immunity.<br> <br>Directions of use:<br>Add 5 scoops (45 gm) to a glass of lukewarm milk (200 ml). <br>Stir until dissolved. <br>Add sugar to taste.<br> <br>Available in Vanilla flavour.<br> <br>Use under medical supervision.</div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/080321_07_53_44.jpg', '', 695.00, NULL, '1 tin of 400 gm powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-08 07:51:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6212, 7, 'Protinex Lite Health And Nutritional Drink Vanilla Zero Sugar', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information </h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Protinex Lite Health And Nutritional Drink Mix For Adults with High protein & High Fiber, Vanilla </span>is ready to serve beverage mix that helps meet the nutrient requirements of Indian Adults. Protinex contains 26 essential vitamins and minerals including 11 immuno nutrients³; that support immunity, build strength and provide energy. With high fibre, high protein, and low GI (Glycemic Index), Protinex Lite is a perfect choice for those who are looking for a healthy and well- balanced lifestyle and weight management**. Available in vanilla flavor, it’s an ideal drink with zero added sugar* that easily makes its place in your everyday diet plan.<br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><br>Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Dietary Fiber</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamin-A,B,E&,C</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>High protein and 11 immuno nutrients help build immunity, build strength and provide energy. Take Protinex daily to support a healthy lifestyle</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Formulated with high protein, high fibre, and low Glycemic Index (GI) to support a healthy and balanced lifestyle</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>ZERO ADDED SUGAR FOR WEIGHT MANAGEMENT: Delicious vanilla flavoured drink with zero added