(7026, 6, 'Similac Infant Formula Stage 1', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Similac Infant Formula Stage 1&nbsp;</span>is a spray-dried stage 1 infant milk substitute for infants up to 6 months. Similac is designed to support normal growth and development. Similac contains a fat blend known to support easy digestion and promote calcium absorption It contains Essential fatty acids, Vitamins and Minerals (such as Calcium and Iron) that are known to support healthy growth and development of the baby. For over 85 years, Similac from Abbott Nutrition has set the standards for science-based infant nutrition and has been nourishing millions of babies worldwide. When your baby is 6 months, try Similac 2, specially formulated to meet the needs of growing infants over 6 months. Infants above 6 months should receive supplemental food in addition to the formula. Consult your doctor for advice.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Omega 3 and 6 fatty acids</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Choline</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Iron</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Taurine</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Iodine</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Folic Acid</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Zinc&nbsp;</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\