(7031, 6, 'Similac IQ+ Infant Formula Stage 1', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information&nbsp;</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Similac IQ+ Infant Formula Stage 1</span>&nbsp;is a spray dried stage 1 infant milk substitute for newborn baby up to 6 months. Similac IQ+ is an infant milk powder designed to support normal growth and development. It contains DHA + Natural Vitamin E, Omega 3, Omega 6, AA, Choline, Iron, Taurine, Iodine, Folic Acid and Zinc that are known to support a baby’s brain and eye development. Similac IQ+ exclusively uses a form of naturally occurring vitamin E. Natural vitamin E is the predominant form found in mother’s milk.&nbsp;<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Ingredients:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Folic acid</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Milk solids</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Maltodextrin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Demineralised whey</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Low erucic rapeseed oil</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Coconut oil</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>High oleic sunflower oil</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Sunflower oil</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Mineral</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Soya lecithin</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Vitamins</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Nucleotides</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Acidity regulator (Citric acid)</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Similac IQ+ 1 is a spray dried stage 1 infant milk substitute for newborn babies up to 6 months</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Similac IQ+ is an infant milk formula that contains DHA + Natural Vitamin E, Omega 3, Omega 6, AA, Choline, Iron, Taurine, Iodine, Folic Acid and Zinc that are known to support a baby’s brain and eye development</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Similac IQ+ exclusively uses a form of naturally occurring vitamin E. Natural vitamin E is the predominant form found in mother’s milk. Vitamin E is an important antioxidant for protecting cells and supporting the development of a baby’s eyes and brain</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Similac IQ+ has a fat blend known to support easy digestion and promote calcium absorption</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Contains essential fatty acids, vitamins and minerals (such as Calcium and Iron) that are known to support the healthy growth of the baby</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Similac IQ+ is an infant milk powder designed to support normal growth and development</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>When the baby is 6 months, try Similac IQ+ 2, specially formulated to meet the needs of growing infants over 6 months. Infants above 6 months should receive supplemental food in addition to the formula. Consult a doctor for advice</li></ul><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Directions For Use:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Add 3 scoops in a bowl and pour around 75 ml lukewarm water into it</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Mix it properly and feed your little one</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/080321_08_39_35.jpg', '', 650.00, NULL, '1 box of 400 gm powder', NULL, 1, '2021-03-08 08:35:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
