(8441, 1, 'Warf 5 Tablet', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Warf 5 Tablet is an oral anticoagulant which helps prevent the formation of harmful blood clots in the legs, lungs, brain and heart. It is used for deep vein thrombosis, pulmonary embolism and stroke prevention.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF WARF TABLET</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Prevention of Blood clots</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Warf 5 Tablet blocks a substance in the body which is involved in blood clotting. Although it does not “dissolve” blood clots, it can prevent them from getting bigger so your body can dissolve them over time. It will also prevent new ones from forming. It keeps your blood flowing freely around your body and makes it less likely that a clot will form inside a blood vessel. This can help prevent or reduce damage caused by stroke, clots in your lungs (pulmonary embolism) or other blood vessels (thrombosis). It can also make it less likely that parts of a clot will break off and travel to other parts of the body. You should take Warf 5 Tablet regularly and make appropriate lifestyle changes to help this medicine be effective.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/050321_08_23_21.jpg', '', 78.96, NULL, '30 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:23:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8442, 1, 'Wax-Off Ear Drop', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Wax-Off Ear Drop has a combination of medicines that is used to treat pain in the ear. It helps in dissolving the ear wax. It provides relief from the pain due to hardened wax.Wax-Off Ear Drop is to be used only in the affected ear in the dose and duration as advised by the doctor. Wash your hands before using this medicine. It is advised to check the label for directions before use. Do not skip any doses and finish the full course of treatment even if you feel better.Stopping the medicine too early may lead to the infection returning or worsening. This medicine is generally safe to use and has minimal side effects. However, if you experience any side effects such as rashes, irritation or any other symptoms for a longer duration which you think are due to this medicine, please consult your doctor.</div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF WAX-OFF EAR DROP</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Softening of earwax</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Wax-Off Ear Drop is a liquid solution which helps to soften, disperse and sometimes dissolve ear wax. Although ear wax drops can be an effective, self-sufficient treatment for ear wax, they are more often used before some other form of treatment for ear wax such as ear syringing or ear irrigation. This medicine is absorbed by ear wax, aiding in thinning and softening it in the process. It also lubricates the inner layers of skin lining the ear canal, enabling its movement towards the entrance of the ear canal. This helps in getting rid of the earwax without pain and discomfort.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/210221_11_32_50.jpg', '', 60.00, NULL, 'Bottle of 10 ml', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:18:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8443, 1, 'Waxonil Activ Ear Drop', '<div style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \" clear=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Waxonil Activ Ear Drop has a combination of medicines that is used to treat pain in the ear. It helps in dissolving the ear wax. It provides relief from the pain due to hardened wax.Waxonil Activ Ear Drop is to be used only in the affected ear in the dose and duration as advised by the doctor. Wash your hands before using this medicine. It is advised to check the label for directions before use. Do not skip any doses and finish the full course of treatment even if you feel better.<br></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF WAXONIL ACTIV EAR DROP</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">In Softening of earwax</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Waxonil Activ Ear Drop is a liquid solution which helps to soften, disperse and sometimes dissolve ear wax. Although ear wax drops can be an effective, self-sufficient treatment for ear wax, they are more often used before some other form of treatment for ear wax such as ear syringing or ear irrigation. This medicine is absorbed by ear wax, aiding in thinning and softening it in the process. It also lubricates the inner layers of skin lining the ear canal, enabling its movement towards the entrance of the ear canal. This helps in getting rid of the earwax without pain and discomfort.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/210221_11_55_53.webp', '', 99.00, NULL, 'Bottle of 10 ml', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:17:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8444, 1, 'Waxort Ear Drop', '<div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \" source=\"\" sans=\"\" pro\",=\"\" verdana,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.208px;\"=\"\"><div class=\"monograph-content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(49, 49, 49); font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 30px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Ear Drop</p></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/050321_08_04_16.jpg', '', 88.00, NULL, '10 ML IN  BOTTLE', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:16:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8445, 1, 'Wellwoman Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">INTRODUCTION</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Wellwoman Health Supplement for Women Tablet</span> has been specifically designed to help safeguard the nutritional needs of women aged 50 and above. Wellwoman contains a comprehensive range of 26 vitamins, minerals, and plant-derived nutrients to support key areas of health important in women over 50, including heart, brain, and eye health. It contains vitamins B6, pantothenic acid, and iron which contribute to the reduction of tiredness and fatigue. Moreover, B12 vitamin contributes to normal metabolism and normal red blood cell formation. <br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Zinc, selenium and vitamins B6, B12, C and D have also been included in the formula as they contribute to the normal function of the immune system</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Wellwoman  provides vitamin C and E which contribute to the protection of cells from oxidative stress plus mineral zinc, which contributes to the maintenance of normal vision</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Wellwoman  contributes to the normal function of the heart. A combination of folic acid, vitamins B6, and B12 contribute to normal homocysteine metabolism and normal red blood cell formation</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Thiamin (vitamin B1), vitamin B6, vitamin B12,  biotin, and vitamin C support the normal function of the nervous system. Moreover, pantothenic acid helps to maintain normal mental performance.</li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/220221_07_14_23.jpg', '', 260.00, NULL, 'STRIP OF 15 TABLETS', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:14:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8446, 1, 'Wepox Safe 4000IU Injection', '<div><div id=\"overview\"><div class=\"DrugPane__content___3-yrB\" style=\"padding: 0px 24px 24px;\"><div class=\"DrugOverview__container___CqA8x\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><h2 class=\"DrugOverview__title___1OwgG\" style=\"font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 16px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">INTRODUCTION</h2><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Wepox Safe 4000IU Injection is a medicine that helps your bone marrow to produce more red blood cells. It is used to treat a type of anemia caused by kidney disease. It is also used to treat anemia caused by cancer chemotherapy and by taking medicines to treat HIV.<br>Wepox Safe 4000IU Injection is given by injection either under the skin or into a vein which will be decided by your doctor. Usually, the injections are given by a nurse or doctor. The dose depends on your body weight and the cause of your anemia. Iron supplements both before and during treatment may make this treatment more effective. Wepox Safe 4000IU Injection needs to be stored in a fridge but used at room temperature.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">USES OF WEPOX SAFE INJECTION</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Anemia due to chronic kidney disease</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Wepox Safe 4000IU Injection is a man-made protein that helps your bone marrow to produce more red blood cells. It is used to treat anemia which is caused by kidney disease in adults and children who are on dialysis. Anemia is a condition where your body does not have enough red blood cells to carry oxygen around your body. This medicine helps reduce weakness and tiredness that you may be experiencing due to anemia. The injection is usually given by a doctor after a dialysis treatment.</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In Anemia due to cancer chemotherapy</span></div><div class=\"DrugOverview__content___22ZBX\" style=\"padding: 8px 0px 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Anemia is a condition where your body does not have enough red blood cells to carry oxygen around your body. Wepox Safe 4000IU Injection is a man-made protein that works by stimulating the bone marrow (soft tissue inside the bones) to produce more red blood cells. The natural human form of this protein may be reduced when you are having chemotherapy to treat some types of cancer. An injection of the medicine can reduce the need to have a blood transfusion. You may also be given iron supplements to make the treatment more effective.</span></div></div></div></div></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/220221_07_31_28.jpg', '', 1898.00, NULL, '0.4 ml in 1 prefilled syringe', NULL, 1, '2021-03-05 08:12:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
