(8559, 1, 'Zecal Fem Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information about Zecal Fem Tablet</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Zecal Fem Tablets contains Elemental Calcium, Vitamin D3, and Isoflavone as active ingredients.<br>- Zecal Fem Tablets is a dietary supplement useful in low blood calcium levels, vitamin D deficiency, bone formation, increase in the force of contraction of the heart, and blood coagulation<br><br>uses of Zecal Fem Tablets:<br>- Provides enough calcium for the formation of healthy bones and teeth<br>- Increases absorption of calcium and phosphorus required for strong bones&nbsp;<br>- Enhances the immunity of the body to fight against infections<br>- Calcium is important for nerve conductivity, muscle contraction, hormone and enzyme secretion, and blood clotting&nbsp;<br><br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/140321_10_21_29.jpg', '', 394.50, NULL, '10 tablets in 1 strip', NULL, 1, '2021-03-14 10:29:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8560, 1, 'Zecal-Gold Tablet', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">New Zecal Gold tablet is used as bone joint supplement.It contains Calcium,Vitamin D3(cholecalciferol)Zinc, Magnesium, Manganese and boron.<br>&nbsp;<br>Role of key ingredients:<br>Calcium is used to prevent or treat low blood calcium levels in people who do not get enough calcium from their diets.Calcium is important for growth and development of bones.&nbsp;<br>Vitamin D3(cholecalciferol)that is used in the absorption of calcium in the blood. Vitamin D3 helps in processing of essential minerals in the body like Calcium and Phosphorus. Lack of Vitamin D3 results in bone weakening, bone pain, and skin diseases.&nbsp;<br>Zinc, Magnesium, Manganese and boron are necessary for bone mineralization and bone matrix formation.The body requires boron for proper metabolism and utilization of various bone-building factors.<br>&nbsp;<br><br></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/140321_10_21_25.jpg', '', 348.50, NULL, '30 tablets in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-14 10:25:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
