(8639, 1, 'Zincitotal Syrup', '<div class=\"ProductDescription__description-heading___YC4aX\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Information</h2></div><div class=\"ProductDescription__description-content___A_qCZ\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Zincitotal Syrup</span>&nbsp;is a supplement of zinc, multivitamin, multimineral and antioxidants. It works by increasing absorption of calcium and phosphorus required for strong bones; metabolizing carbohydrate thus maintains normal growth. It assists in maintaining many tissues of the body to prevent vitamin B12 deficiency, producing antibodies and hemoglobin by keeping blood sugar level in normal range.<br><br><br><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Key Benefits:</span><br><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Zincitotal syrup treats, controls and prevents anaemia, anorexia and acne</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>Treats diseases caused by vitamin deficiencies</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It\'s used to treat osteoporosis and rheumatitis</li></ul><ul style=\"padding-left: 5px;\"><li>It\'s also used for migraines</li><li></li></ul></div>', 'https://4med.in/public/assets/images/product/130321_11_39_18.jpg', '', 130.00, NULL, '200 ml in 1 bottle', NULL, 1, '2021-03-13 11:18:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
